xt-stroke-width: 0px;\">老婆：“谁让你出来穿这件黑色衣服，黑色吸热。”</span><br style=\"font: 16px/30px Simsun; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><span style=\"font: 16px/30px Simsun; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">老公道：“不怪那个，我穿的白衬衣也热啊。”</span><br style=\"font: 16px/30px Simsun; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><span style=\"font: 16px/30px Simsun; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">老婆：“你长的黑，也吸热。”</span></p><p style=\"display:none;\" class=\"cloudreamHelperLink\" codetype=\"post\" entryid=\"2110\"></p>','','ADMIN','1423634412.61',NULL,NULL,1),(1843,'段子里的逗B乐死人','<p> 1、A：能不能用2个字来形容女孩子漂亮？</p><p>    B：已撸。</p><p>2、恋爱时：男：“想吃吗？”</p><p>   女：“不想。”结婚后：</p><p>   女：“我想吃这个。”</p><p>   男：“吃什么吃，胖的跟猪似的。”</p><p>3、问：为什么有人说“女人永远是对的”?</p><p>   答：按照达尔文的进化论