了，忽然看见远处有一点红光，唉，又忘关电源了。用手一按，艹艹艹，没有烧完的蚊香。。。<br>2、一个朋友小时侯上山放牛。<br>恰巧遇到一帮公安在山上义务植树，干活热都把外衣脱了，有个领导没脱外衣在休息。<br>这货冲上去就和这领导说话：叔啊，领着劳改犯干活呢？<br>干活的民警满腔黑线啊！<br>3、咖啡店，一位美女走过来对我说：“帅哥，有充电宝吗？”<br>我摊开空空的双手对她说：“你瞎吗？” <br>她说：“对不起，丑B，有充电宝吗？”<br>4、今天早上在一个陌生的地方吃早点，吃的油条。<br>吃完后去结账，老板正忙。我想找餐巾纸擦擦手，看见一个纸盒子，以为是放餐巾纸的，就顺手掀开了。<br>哇！满满的一盒子钞票，我没来及伸手，老板瞬间就捂住了……<br>那啥，听我说，我不是想偷钱，真不是……</p><p style=\"display:none;\" class=\"cloudreamHelperLink\" codetype=\"post\" entryid=\"2139\"></p>','','ADMIN','1423634421.66',NULL,NULL,1),(1870,'没带钱，走买衣服去！','<p> <span style=\"font: 16px/30px Simsun; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">那天和老公逛街，路过一个时装店，看到里面的衣服真不错，顿时就有了买欲。</span><br style=\"font: 16px/30px Simsun; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><span style=\"font: 16px/30px Simsun; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">我对老公说：“这家的衣服真漂亮，咱进去逛逛。”</span><br style=\"font: 16px/30px Simsun; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><span style=\"font: 16px/30px Simsun; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">老公：“逛什么逛，这种店里面的衣服都超级的贵，你带钱了没有？”</span><br style=\"font: 16px/30px Simsun; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><span style=\"font: 16px/30px Simsun; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">我一看钱包没多少钱，说：“没有。”</span><br style=\"font: 16px/30px Simsun; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><span style=\"font: 16px/30px Simsun; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">老公：“那走，进去逛逛。”</span></p><p style=\"display:none;\" class=\"cloudreamHelperLink\" codetype=\"post\" entryid=\"2137\"></p>','','ADMIN','1423634421.97',NULL,NULL,1),(1871,'好了，不说了，该录口供了','<p> <span style=\"font: 18px/28.78px 宋体; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">　回家的路上，我开着60码的车速，后面的车一直想超车，还不停的打喇叭，没办法，我打开车窗把给表弟买的玩具枪朝后面指了指，那车直接一个刹车，停住了，哈哈，真好笑。好了，不说了，该录口供了。</span></p><p style=\"display:none;\" class=\"cloudreamHelperLink\" codetype=\"post\" entryid=\"2132\"></p>','','ADMIN','1423634422.24',NULL,NULL,1),(1872,'笑爆了的婚恋冷幽默','<p> 1、男友对我说：“我会照顾你一辈子，我有十块钱肯给你用九块。”<br>我问他：“如果你有十万呢？”<br>男友：“那我就把十块钱都给你！”<br>2、新郎到酒店迎娶新娘，接亲的时侯，新娘的闺蜜们在房里嚷着要“开门红包”。<br>新郎一摸口袋，糟糕，忘带了。无耐，他百般求情，可求了半天，还是没把门求开。<br>正当新郎着急上火时，只见伴郎淡定地拿出房卡，在感应器上一刷，“滴”的一声，门开了。。。<br>3、一对恋人是异地恋，聚少离多。这次，男的临走时这对恋人算了算，还有78天才能相会，于是给女友买了78袋零食，对她说：“你每天吃一袋，吃完了我就回来了。”<br>不料，一周后，男的有个意外的机会，回到女孩的城市。<br>两人见面时，女的激动的说：“你果然没有骗我，我刚吃完这些零食你就回来了。”<br>4、男孩首次拜见女友父母，女友妈妈问他：“小伙子，你都有过啥理想？”<br>他道：“小学的时侯，当小吃店老板是我的理想；初中的时侯，当游戏厅老板是我的理想；大学的时侯，当个酒吧老板是我的理想；现在，有个丈母娘是我唯一的理想。”</p><p style=\"display:none;\" class=\"cloudreamHelperLink\" codetype=\"post\" entryid=\"2140\"></p>','','ADMIN','1423634422.48',NULL,NULL,1),(1873,'打击到老公了','<p> <span style=\"font: 18px/28.78px 宋体; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">老公在高歌《晚秋》，唱完，他得意地问我：“怎么样？我这嗓音，像不像毛宁？”</span><br style=\"font: 18px/28.78px 宋体; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: currentColor; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><span style=\"font: 18px/28.78px 宋体; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">　　我：“挺好，虽然不像他，但好歹像姓毛的！”</span><br style=\"font: 18px/28.78px 宋体; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: currentColor; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><span style=\"font: 18px/28.78px 宋体; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">　　他不禁纳闷：“哪个姓毛的？”</span><br style=\"font: 18px/28.78px 宋体; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: currentColor; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><span style=\"font: 18px/28.78px 宋体; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">　　我嘿嘿一笑：“毛驴。”</span></p><p style=\"display:none;\" class=\"cloudreamHelperLink\" codetype=\"post\" entryid=\"2133\"></p>','','ADMIN','1423634422.75',NULL,NULL,1),(1874,'好有追求的小动物','<p> 1、看到最新的竖版地图，蜗牛道：“爸爸，我长大了，要当兵，为祖国巡逻边疆! ”<br>老蜗牛听了，点点头，问：“你说的是在地图上巡逻吗？”<br>2、小蝌蚪曾经以为自己将来会是一只漂亮的金鱼，或是一只威武的螃蟹，也可能是一只悠闲的乌龟，最后才了解自己是一只丑丑的青蛙，心中难免失落。<br>青蛙妈妈安慰道：“知足吧，没变成一只蛤蟆就不错了。”<br>3、小狗对爸爸说：“我想学外科医生！”<br>“为什么？”<br>“如果有人截肢，我不就多了一份口粮嘛！”<br>4、小蚊子对爸爸说：我要报考军校！<br>噢！爸爸问：你不怕吃苦么？ <br>小蚊子道：不怕！我从小就立志做一名针插兵！</p><p style=\"display:none;\" class=\"cloudreamHelperLink\" codetype=\"post\" entryid=\"2141\"></p>','','ADMIN','1423634423.02',NULL,NULL,1),(1875,'人生路上，无论怎样，我们都要走下去','<p> <span style=\"font: 18px/28.78px 宋体; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">　雨，有急，有缓；路，有平，有坎。世上的事，有顺，有逆；人生的情，有喜，有悲。顺境，不要得意，狂妄傲慢，喜悦能够持续；逆境，不要气馁，绝望悲戚，事情还有转机。人生路上，无论怎样，我们都要走下去。荣也好，辱也吧，坦然面对，心平气静，安然于得失，淡然于成败，依旧向前。</span></p><p style=\"display:none;\" class=\"cloudreamHelperLink\" codetype=\"post\" entryid=\"2135\"></p>','','ADMIN','1423634423.32',NULL,NULL,1),(1876,'一切都在变化','<p>         <span style=\"font: 18px/28.78px 宋体; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">大二的时候我们三个人经常在一起，我，我女友，我室友。</span><br style=\"font: 18px/28.78px 宋体; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: currentColor; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><span style=\"font: 18px/28.78px 宋体; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">　　大三了，我们三个还是经常在一起，我，我室友，他女朋友。</span></p><p style=\"display:none;\" class=\"cloudreamHelperLink\" codetype=\"post\" entryid=\"2131\"></p>','','ADMIN','1423634423.63',NULL,NULL,1),(1877,'爆笑小两口，贫嘴的一天天','<p> </p><p><br>1、老婆对老公抱怨道：“每天早上你一起床就说‘困死了’，叫你做点家务你说‘累死了’，饭做得晚了些你说‘饿死了’，乘公共汽车上下班你说‘挤死了’，让你打的你说‘贵死了’，骑自行车你又说‘冷死了’……你这一天到晚要死几回呀？”<br>老公道：“烦死了！”</p><p> <br>2、一对年轻夫妻，老公说：“亲爱的，以后我出门上班，你要说恭送老公，下班回家你要说臣妾叩见老公，祝老公万福金安！”<br>老婆不屑，说“你想得美，天天让我跪着给你请安，那你准备怎么报答我？”<br>老公皱着眉头想了半天，然后一本正经说：“我保证今后只翻你一个人的牌子。”</p><p></p><p style=\"display:none;\" class=\"cloudreamHelperLink\" codetype=\"post\" entryid=\"2136\"></p>','','ADMIN','1423634423.81',NULL,NULL,1),(1878,'老舅买的阿迪达斯','<p> <span style=font: 15px/28px \"Microsoft YaHei\", 微软雅黑; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;>老舅在阿迪达斯实体店买双鞋，800多回头在网上找一模一样的才400多。我老舅就又在网上买了双，然后把实体店的退了，我跟老舅说，网上的是便宜可能是高仿的！我老舅说没事，我把网上买的退给实体店了。。</span></p><p style=\"display:none;\" class=\"cloudreamHelperLink\" codetype=\"post\" entryid=\"2142\"></p>','','ADMIN','1423634424.07',NULL,NULL,1),(1879,'老爸被鄙视了','<p> <span style=\"font: 18px/28.78px 宋体; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">有一次我爸带着我家傻狗去遛弯，玩了一会回家了。走到四楼傻狗不走了就在门口不走了转圈，我爸骂骂咧咧的喊了几句，傻狗还是不走，我爸就上五楼了。</span><br style=\"font: 18px/28.78px 宋体; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: currentColor; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><span style=\"font: 18px/28.78px 宋体; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">　　结果，是我爸走错楼层了…下来的时候傻狗斜眼看他的。</span></p><p style=\"display:none;\" class=\"cloudreamHelperLink\" codetype=\"post\" entryid=\"2143\"></p>','','ADMIN','1423634424.38',NULL,NULL,1),(1880,'唐僧笑话大全','<p> </p><p style=\"font: 14px/2em 宋体; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: normal; word-wrap: normal; min-height: 1.5em; max-width: 100%; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 2em; word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%;\">1．清晨，唐僧从梦中醒来，发现孙悟空跪在自己的床前，于是便问：“悟空，你怎么了？”孙悟空满脸泪水的说：“师傅，我求您了，下次说梦话，不念紧箍咒，行吗？”</span></p><p style=\"font: 14px/2em 宋体; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: normal; word-wrap: normal; min-height: 1.5em; max-width: 100%; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><br>	 </p><p style=\"font: 14px/2em 宋体; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: normal; word-wrap: normal; min-height: 1.5em; max-width: 100%; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><br>	2．悟空因三打白骨精被唐僧贬回花果山，几个月后猪八戒突然来访，进门就哭。悟空问：“队伍到哪儿了？”八戒答：“临汾。”悟空又问：“可是又遇见妖精？”八戒答：”没有。”悟空急：“那你哭什么？”八戒更加伤心：“大师兄，你快回去吧！师父被人卖到黑砖窑去了，我们都找了仨月了。”</p><p style=\"font: 14px/2em 宋体; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: normal; word-wrap: normal; min-height: 1.5em; max-width: 100%; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><br>	 </p><p style=\"font: 14px/2em 宋体; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: normal; word-wrap: normal; min-height: 1.5em; max-width: 100%; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><br>	3．取经队伍到达贫困地区，几天化不到斋，悟空因为要保护师父，只好让沙僧和八戒去远处城里找吃的。第一天去，都空手回来，因为没有钱。第二天去，还是空手，因为没有钱。悟空大怒：“再找不到吃的，就别回来！”第三天傍晚，沙僧高高兴兴地背着一大袋子米，还剩了好多钱。悟空大喜，又问：“八戒呢？”沙僧顿时伤心地哭道：“大师兄，原谅我吧，咱们这么多人，就二师兄能卖到16块钱一斤!”</p><p style=\"font: 14px/2em 宋体; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: normal; word-wrap: normal; min-height: 1.5em; max-width: 100%; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><br>	 </p><p style=\"font: 14px/2em 宋体; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: normal; word-wrap: normal; min-height: 1.5em; max-width: 100%; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><br>	4．师徒四人到达一个大城市，悟空化斋，沙僧收拾行李，八戒出去遛马。晚上八戒空手而归，唐僧问：“白龙马呢？”八戒说：“被交警扣了。”唐僧问为什么？八戒说：“它放了个屁。”唐僧说：“放个屁也不至于被扣啊？”八戒说：“警察说北京要办绿色奥运，它尾气超标了。”</p><p style=\"font: 14px/2em 宋体; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: normal; word-wrap: normal; min-height: 1.5em; max-width: 100%; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><br>	 </p><p style=\"font: 14px/2em 宋体; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: normal; word-wrap: normal; min-height: 1.5em; max-width: 100%; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><br>	5．悟空化缘回来发现师父不见了，沙僧和八戒在地上哭。悟空问：“师父呢？”八戒说：“丢了。”悟空说：“快去找呀！”沙僧说：“到处找遍了，没有。”悟空又找了一圈，也没有找到。三个人正发愁，忽然悟空问：“师父这个月房贷交了吗？”沙僧说：“没有。”“养路费交了吗？”“也没有。”悟空说：“都洗洗睡吧，师父跑不了，有银行跟交警看着呢！”</p><p style=\"font: 14px/2em 宋体; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: normal; word-wrap: normal; min-height: 1.5em; max-width: 100%; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><br>	 </p><p style=\"font: 14px/2em 宋体; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: normal; word-wrap: normal; min-height: 1.5em; max-width: 100%; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><br>	6．唐僧师徒路过狮驼岭，狮子精抓了唐僧，悟空费尽千心万苦，终于战败了狮子精。正欲打死，、突然文殊菩萨来到，说那是他的坐骑，带了狮子精扬长而去。悟空大骂。八戒劝道：“算了吧大师兄，人家是领导的司机，也算公务员呢。”</p><p style=\"font: 14px/2em 宋体; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: normal; word-wrap: normal; min-height: 1.5em; max-width: 100%; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><br>	 </p><p style=\"font: 14px/2em 宋体; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: normal; word-wrap: normal; min-height: 1.5em; max-width: 100%; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><br>	7．唐僧师徒到了西天门外，见500罗汉背着行李往外走，忙问何故？众罗汉叹气说：“你不知道，再过几天，新《劳动法》就实行了，我们这些临时工都被遣散了。” 唐僧问：“菩萨们呢？”罗汉说：“他们日子也不好过，西天为了规避新《劳动法》，都强迫他们跟XX公司签约了，以后就是第三方公司外派到西天工作的。”</p><p style=\"font: 14px/2em 宋体; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: normal; word-wrap: normal; min-height: 1.5em; max-width: 100%; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><br>	 </p><p style=\"font: 14px/2em 宋体; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: normal; word-wrap: normal; min-height: 1.5em; max-width: 100%; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><br>	8．唐僧等人取经有功，被封为菩萨佛爷，几人高高兴兴到西天各处找房子，几天后败兴而归。唐僧说：“咱哥儿几个还是回去吧，西天房价太高，咱连首付都交不起。”沙僧说：“不是听说有经济适用房么？要不咱问问去？”悟空说：“傻兄弟，西天大大小小的领导，谁没几个亲戚？能轮到咱们？”</p><p style=\"font: 14px/2em 宋体; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: normal; word-wrap: normal; min-height: 1.5em; max-width: 100%; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><br>	 </p><p style=\"font: 14px/2em 宋体; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: normal; word-wrap: normal; min-height: 1.5em; max-width: 100%; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><br>	9．八戒最近几天闷闷不乐，晚上瞅着月亮发呆．悟空知道他的心事，利用双休日到月宫访问了一圈儿，回来后对八戒说：“傻兄弟！我去问过了，中国发射的是一颗卫星，还没派人登月呢。一个机器，你吃啥醋啊！”</p><p style=\"font: 14px/2em 宋体; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: normal; word-wrap: normal; min-height: 1.5em; max-width: 100%; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><br>	 </p><p style=\"font: 14px/2em 宋体; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: normal; word-wrap: normal; min-height: 1.5em; max-width: 100%; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><br>	10．唐僧取来真经，背着去见李世民。唐僧说：“大哥，我回来了。”李世民：“哦。”唐僧说：“真经我取来了!”李世民说：“哦，放那儿吧。”唐僧说：“大哥，我费了十几年工夫，辛辛苦苦办了这么大事儿，你咋还不高兴呢？嫌我差旅费高了？”李世民摘下耳机说：“你那些经文，我用迅雷下了一小时就下完了 ! 早知道电脑这么厉害，我当初还让你去干吗呀！?”</p><p style=\"font: 14px/2em 宋体; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: normal; word-wrap: normal; min-height: 1.5em; max-width: 100%; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><br>	 </p><p style=\"font: 14px/2em 宋体; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: normal; word-wrap: normal; min-height: 1.5em; max-width: 100%; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><br>	11．一大群小妖精扛着被捆成粽子的唐僧，兴冲冲走进洞内，高喊：“大王！大王！我们终于抓住唐僧了！”老妖精从睡梦中被吵醒，抬眼看了一眼，无精打采地说：“送回去吧。”小妖精奇怪地问为什么。老妖精说：“报纸上说唐僧肉里含有致癌物质!”</p><p style=\"font: 14px/2em 宋体; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: normal; word-wrap: normal; min-height: 1.5em; max-width: 100%; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><br>	 </p><p style=\"font: 14px/2em 宋体; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: normal; word-wrap: normal; min-height: 1.5em; max-width: 100%; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><br>	12．猪八戒取经之后去整容变成一个特别帅气的小伙子，然后他去酒吧找小姐喝酒，出来之后对那个小姐说：“你知道吗？你知道我以前多磕碜吗？我以前是猪八戒你知道吗？”小姐看看他满脸哭容的说：“二师兄，我是沙僧啊！”..</p><p></p><p style=\"display:none;\" class=\"cloudreamHelperLink\" codetype=\"post\" entryid=\"2145\"></p>','','ADMIN','1423634424.7',NULL,NULL,1),(1881,'我好像说错了些什么','<p> <span style=font: 15px/28px \"Microsoft YaHei\", 微软雅黑; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;>本人男，跟新同事出差，晚上一起住宾馆，他比较内向，我俩就互相看着对方一句话也没说。气氛有些尴尬，于是我首先开口道：“你很闷啊！ ” 他扭捏了半天有些不好意思地说：“你也很men啊！ ”说着把手放到了我的腿上！我好像说错了些什么…</span></p><p style=\"display:none;\" class=\"cloudreamHelperLink\" codetype=\"post\" entryid=\"2146\"></p>','','ADMIN','1423634424.98',NULL,NULL,1),(1882,'瞬间笑喷你的小雷神','<p> </p><p>1、同事问儿子：“小朋友，你属什么呀？”<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">儿子一本正经的答道：“叔叔，我属鸡蛋。”<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">同事一愣，忙问：“为什么属鸡蛋呀？”<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">儿子振振有词的说：“我妈妈属鸡，我是她儿子，当然属鸡蛋啦！”</p><p style=\"font: 14px/23px 宋体; margin: 0px; padding: 6px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">2、一对夫妻吵架，女的一气之下回娘家了。<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">男的逗他五岁的儿子说：“儿子，你妈走了，我再给你找个妈妈要不要。”<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">儿子问：“她会打我吗？”<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">男的说：“不会”<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">儿子：“她会不让我玩游戏吗？”<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">男：“不会”<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">儿子马上来一句：“把锁换了，别让妈妈再回来了。”</p><p style=\"font: 14px/23px 宋体; margin: 0px; padding: 6px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">3、老婆同事有一个小男孩，在家里不好好吃饭，他奶奶就给他说：“不好好吃饭以后就娶不着漂亮媳妇。”<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">小屁孩抬起头看了看他奶奶说：“我爷爷以前是不是也不好好吃饭？”</p><p style=\"font: 14px/23px 宋体; margin: 0px; padding: 6px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">4、今天做公交车去上班，来了一个小女孩对我说：“叔叔，你能给我让个座吗？”<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">看到萌萌的小女孩我绅士的给她让了座，并期待她的回应。<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">没想到她来了句：“叔叔，虽然你长得不咋的但还是挺懂事的。”</p><p style=\"font: 14px/23px 宋体; margin: 0px; padding: 6px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">5、儿子分床后总想找个理由跟妈妈睡，一次儿子又赖在大人床上不走。<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">妈妈问他为何不自己睡去，儿子狡辩地说：“一个人睡不着，想找个女的陪陪。”</p><p></p><p style=\"display:none;\" class=\"cloudreamHelperLink\" codetype=\"post\" entryid=\"2147\"></p>','','ADMIN','1423634425.26',NULL,NULL,1),(1883,'巨幽默的老爸和老妈','<p> </p><p style=\"font: 14px/23px 宋体; margin: 0px; padding: 6px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">1、今天早晨老爸在刮胡子，老妈说：“天天没事老刮胡子干嘛？”<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">老爸回了一句：“它不让我露脸，我就不让它露头！”</p><p style=\"font: 14px/23px 宋体; margin: 0px; padding: 6px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">2、老妈对我说：“以后出门，不要喊我妈妈，要喊我姐姐。”<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">我：“为什么？”<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">老妈笑道：“那显得我多年轻呀！”<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">老爸在一边来了一句：“要显年轻，应该喊奶奶。”</p><p style=\"font: 14px/23px 宋体; margin: 0px; padding: 6px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">3、某天晚上，也不是很晚，但天已经黑了，我妈突然要去我外婆家（不是很远）有点事，我爸就说：“我陪你去吧。”<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">我妈问：“为什么？”<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">我爸：“这么晚了，怕遇上打劫的~”<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">我妈像是抓住把柄了：“你不是说我长的这个样子劫匪都不敢碰我吗？”<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">我爸灰常淡定的说：“这么晚了，我怕劫匪看不清。。。”</p><p style=\"font: 14px/23px 宋体; margin: 0px; padding: 6px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">4、老妈禁止老爸打麻将，那天老爸偷偷地打麻将打到很晚才回家，老妈劈头就问：打麻将了吗？<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">老爸说：没打！<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">老妈问：赢钱了没？<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">老爸说：赢了！</p><p style=\"font: 14px/23px 宋体; margin: 0px; padding: 6px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">5、老妈强制老爸戒烟，晚饭后老爸烟瘾来了，趁老妈洗碗在门口偷抽，也许是抽的太忘情了，最后一口还没吐完就进门，正好被老妈看到。。。<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">老妈：“你干嘛呢！”<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">老爸：“我没抽烟！！！”<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">老妈：“那你吐的是什么！”<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">老爸：“浮云。。。”</p><p style=\"font: 14px/23px 宋体; margin: 0px; padding: 6px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">6、话说老爸老妈闲着没事，在家拌嘴，不知道老爸说了句什么，老妈说老爸“你说你像话吗？”<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">只听老爸幽幽的说了句“像画，像画早挂墙上了”</p><p></p><p style=\"display:none;\" class=\"cloudreamHelperLink\" codetype=\"post\" entryid=\"2148\"></p>','','ADMIN','1423634425.57',NULL,NULL,1),(1884,'专黑理发师','<p> </p><p style=\"font: 14px/23px 宋体; margin: 0px; padding: 6px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">1、我已剪短我的发，剪断了牵挂，可你却还要我办张卡！</p><p style=\"font: 14px/23px 宋体; margin: 0px; padding: 6px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">2、 盲人按摩都已经得到社会认可了，哑巴怎么还不开理发店当理发师？</p><p style=\"font: 14px/23px 宋体; margin: 0px; padding: 6px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">3、理发师的一生：年轻时不能自理，老了也是。</p><p style=\"font: 14px/23px 宋体; margin: 0px; padding: 6px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">4、理发师与妈妈其实有一个共同点。理发师永远不懂一厘米的长度。妈妈盛饭时永远不懂半碗的深度。还有唯一不同点，前者让我们失望，后者让我们感动。</p><p style=\"font: 14px/23px 宋体; margin: 0px; padding: 6px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">5、一哥们头发自然卷很严重，一日去理发店和理发师说怎么剪怎么剪，巴拉巴拉说了一堆。<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">理发师听完说道：老弟呀，你这头发要是这么剪，就白烫了…</p><p style=\"font: 14px/23px 宋体; margin: 0px; padding: 6px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">6、哥们到理发店理发，对接待小姐拿出一张毛爷爷，说照着这个剪，意思是找个100价位的理发师，头发剪完了，理发师给他剪了一个毛爷爷的发型...</p><p style=\"font: 14px/23px 宋体; margin: 0px; padding: 6px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">7、前不久咱去理发...一坐下什么都没说，理发师开口了：“兄弟你这头发有头屑”<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">我：“嗯”<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">理发师：“不过还好啦，没有白头发！”<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">我：“嗯”<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">理发师：“我见过很多种类的头发，有油发、黄发、稀发........”<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">我：“嗯，嗯。”<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">理发师：“你这头发太干燥，以我多年经验来看。是‘沙’发！”</p><p style=\"font: 14px/23px 宋体; margin: 0px; padding: 6px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">8、老公去剪头发，理发师对于我老公非常客气，各种聊家常“以前没见过你呀帅哥你平常不来吗你喜欢理什么发型要不要办张卡我们这里办卡全年洗头八折帅哥要不要考虑下”<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">老公淡淡道“之前在隔壁办了张卡，到期了就没续费。”<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">理发师忙问“为什么没续费呢你觉得我们店和隔壁比起来有什么优点吗？”<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">老公仍是淡淡道“因为隔壁的理发师嘴太碎，很讨厌。”……</p><p></p><p style=\"display:none;\" class=\"cloudreamHelperLink\" codetype=\"post\" entryid=\"2149\"></p>','','ADMIN','1423634425.84',NULL,NULL,1),(1885,'越活越清醒,越清醒感觉越悲催','<p> </p><p style=\"font: 14px/23px 宋体; margin: 0px; padding: 6px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">1、每一句“我开玩笑的”话里都有几分真意。</p><p style=\"font: 14px/23px 宋体; margin: 0px; padding: 6px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">2、准备恶语伤人的时候我们便会加上一句“都是为了你好”。</p><p style=\"font: 14px/23px 宋体; margin: 0px; padding: 6px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">3、其实对于绝大多数人来说，打工是能够赚钱最多的方式。</p><p style=\"font: 14px/23px 宋体; margin: 0px; padding: 6px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">4、很多人自称吃货，那主要是因为笨。很多人自称女汉子，那主要是因为长的不好看。</p><p style=\"font: 14px/23px 宋体; margin: 0px; padding: 6px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">5、有钱而奢侈是贵族的奢华，有钱而朴素是低调的内涵；没钱而奢侈是赤裸裸的装B，没钱而朴素是穷得真没辙了。</p><p style=\"font: 14px/23px 宋体; margin: 0px; padding: 6px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">6、秋天是收获的季节。别人的收获是成功与快乐，你的收获是认识到并不是每个人都会成功与快乐。</p><p style=\"font: 14px/23px 宋体; margin: 0px; padding: 6px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">7、人生就是这样，有欢笑也有泪水。一部分人主要负责欢笑，另一部分人主要负责泪水。</p><p style=\"font: 14px/23px 宋体; margin: 0px; padding: 6px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">8、精英阶层一边啃着心灵鸡腿和心灵鸡胸，一边为我们送上来心灵鸡汤，说人生的价值并不在于你挣了多少钱和外在是否美。</p><p style=\"font: 14px/23px 宋体; margin: 0px; padding: 6px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">9、当你用：“没关系，至少你尽力了”来安慰别人的失败，实际上你在说：“连你最好的表现都是坨垃圾”。</p><p style=\"font: 14px/23px 宋体; margin: 0px; padding: 6px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">10、人分两类：一类是节俭得仿佛永远要活下去似的；另一类则奢侈得仿佛明天就要死去似的。</p><p></p><p style=\"display:none;\" class=\"cloudreamHelperLink\" codetype=\"post\" entryid=\"2150\"></p>','','ADMIN','1423634426.12',NULL,NULL,1),(1886,'这真是有效的还击啊','<p><span style=\"font: 18px/28.78px 宋体; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">老公去剪头发，理发师对于我老公非常客气，各种聊家常“以前没见过你呀帅哥你平常不来吗你喜欢理什么发型要不要办张卡我们这里办卡全年洗头八折帅哥要不要考虑下”</span><br style=\"font: 18px/28.78px 宋体; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: currentColor; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><span style=\"font: 18px/28.78px 宋体; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">　　老公淡淡道“之前在隔壁办了张卡，到期了就没续费。”</span><br style=\"font: 18px/28.78px 宋体; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: currentColor; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><span style=\"font: 18px/28.78px 宋体; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">　　理发师忙问“为什么没续费呢你觉得我们店和隔壁比起来有什么优点吗？”</span><br style=\"font: 18px/28.78px 宋体; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: currentColor; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><span style=\"font: 18px/28.78px 宋体; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">　　老公仍是淡淡道“因为隔壁的理发师嘴太碎，很讨厌。”……</span></p><p style=\"display:none;\" class=\"cloudreamHelperLink\" codetype=\"post\" entryid=\"2151\"></p>','','ADMIN','1423634426.74',NULL,NULL,1),(1887,'纸人','<p><span style=\"font: 18px/28.78px 宋体; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">在一次聚会上，他看见了她。只一眼，便钟情。</span><br style=\"font: 18px/28.78px 宋体; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: currentColor; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><span style=\"font: 18px/28.78px 宋体; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">　　她是那么的美，洁白的皮肤、红润的脸蛋和嘴唇，轻盈瘦小的身子仿佛风一吹就会飘走。他决定带她回去，她只是笑着，不说话。</span><br style=\"font: 18px/28.78px 宋体; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: currentColor; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><span style=\"font: 18px/28.78px 宋体; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">　　终于，他不顾众人的嘈杂的反对和异样的眼光，牵着她跑回了自己的家。</span><br style=\"font: 18px/28.78px 宋体; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: currentColor; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><span style=\"font: 18px/28.78px 宋体; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">　　从此，他每天和她腻在一起，欣赏她的美，不可自拔。他家人对他的行为感到不满，说他是被鬼迷了心窍，甚至骂她是个妖精。但她依然温柔，只是笑着，不反驳。他相信她也是深爱着他的。</span><br style=\"font: 18px/28.78px 宋体; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: currentColor; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><span style=\"font: 18px/28.78px 宋体; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">　　他愈加感到她的完美，愈加不可自拔。既然家人不认可，他决定带她离开，去找一个没有世俗眼光的地方与她厮守。他把自己的想法告诉她，她依旧只是微微笑着，没有反对。他相信无论自己去哪里，她都愿意跟随，他们是那么的相爱。</span><br style=\"font: 18px/28.78px 宋体; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: currentColor; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><span style=\"font: 18px/28.78px 宋体; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">　　他带着她穿过车水马龙的城市、穿过人群，她轻盈的身体紧紧跟随着他。街上每个人都用异样的眼光看着他和她，他想，一定是这些人无法欣赏她的美，或者是嫉妒。他更加坚定了自己的信念，要带她去一个没有人的地方，保护她不受到伤害。</span><br style=\"font: 18px/28.78px 宋体; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: currentColor; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><span style=\"font: 18px/28.78px 宋体; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">　　不知跑了多久，他疲了乏了，终于在一处没有人烟的荒野停了下来。他和她相拥着，他问她：“跟我跑出来，你后悔吗？”她仍然回应给他迷人的微笑。只有他能读懂她微笑中的含义。</span><br style=\"font: 18px/28.78px 宋体; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: currentColor; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><span style=\"font: 18px/28.78px 宋体; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">　　夜色越来越沉，空气越来越冷。他在旁边生起一堆火，然后紧紧抱住她，希望能暂时熬过这一夜。可是越是接近黎明，天越黑、空气越冷，眼看着火快要熄灭，他已经冻得不行了，没有力气再起来去找柴禾。他身体在颤抖，嘴唇已经冻得发紫。</span><br style=\"font: 18px/28.78px 宋体; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: currentColor; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><span style=\"font: 18px/28.78px 宋体; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">　　他依旧紧紧抱住她，对她说：“天亮就好了了，我们一定能熬过去的。”她没说话，却站起来向那堆快要熄灭的火走去。他看着她脸上从没改变过的微笑，突然觉得是那么的不真实，像是刻意画上去的。他迷茫了，没有拉住她，看着她走进火里。</span><br style=\"font: 18px/28.78px 宋体; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: currentColor; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><span style=\"font: 18px/28.78px 宋体; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">　　她走进火里后，火突然旺起来了，他感到一阵暖意，脸也被火光映得发红。他想，她是那么深爱着他，宁愿燃烧了自己给他取暖。多么伟大的爱情啊，能让她牺牲了自己。</span><br style=\"font: 18px/28.78px 宋体; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: currentColor; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><span style=\"font: 18px/28.78px 宋体; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">　　那火毕竟只能燃一时，火一熄灭，凉意又袭上全身。他开始后悔没拉住她，如果她还在，他们至少还能抱着互相取暖。他思维渐渐模糊起来，到最后甚至想不起 来到底是她自己走进火里的，还是自己把她推进火里的。难道爱情不是为对方牺牲，而是为了自己而牺牲对方吗？他还来不及清理太多思绪，就失去了意识。</span><br style=\"font: 18px/28.78px 宋体; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: currentColor; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><span style=\"font: 18px/28.78px 宋体; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">　　第二天，他家人终于在城郊的荒野找到了他。他们在议论着：</span><br style=\"font: 18px/28.78px 宋体; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: currentColor; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><span style=\"font: 18px/28.78px 宋体; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">　　这孩纸真傻，不知道是不是被鬼迷了心窍，自从在那次葬礼上看见一个纸人，就变得疯疯癫癫了。</span><br style=\"font: 18px/28.78px 宋体; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: currentColor; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><span style=\"font: 18px/28.78px 宋体; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">　　还把那个纸人带回家，说要跟它在一起。刚请了道士回来看，他竟然带着纸人跑了。</span><br style=\"font: 18px/28.78px 宋体; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: currentColor; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><span style=\"font: 18px/28.78px 宋体; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">　　幸好没跑太远，要不然还不知道会出什么事。</span><br style=\"font: 18px/28.78px 宋体; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: currentColor; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><span style=\"font: 18px/28.78px 宋体; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">　　不过也没傻透，冷得受不了的时候还知道把纸人烧了来取暖。</span><br style=\"font: 18px/28.78px 宋体; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: currentColor; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><span style=\"font: 18px/28.78px 宋体; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">　　…………</span></p><p style=\"display:none;\" class=\"cloudreamHelperLink\" codetype=\"post\" entryid=\"2144\"></p>','','ADMIN','1423634426.79',NULL,NULL,1),(1888,'逗比的小朋友，大人听了年轻10岁。','<p> </p><p style=\"font: 16px/30px Simsun; margin: 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">1.老师让孩子们以《妈妈，我只有一个》写一篇作文。<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">一个同学写道：“昨天我放学回家，很饿，进了厨房，开始翻冰箱，结果发现里面只剩下一个面包，我就拿出来吃了起来，这时妈妈看到了，对我说：‘给我也拿一个面包。’。我回答说：妈妈，我只有一个。”</p><p style=\"font: 16px/30px Simsun; margin: 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">2.饭桌上，妈妈对女儿说：“宝贝，你要多吃一些不同颜色的菜，书上说颜色的种类越多，营养成分就越全。明白吗？”<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">女儿：“明白。”<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">妈妈：“你数下今晚上的菜有几种颜色。”<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">女儿仔细看了看，说：“6种，算上烧焦的部分就是7种。。。。”</p><p></p><p style=\"display:none;\" class=\"cloudreamHelperLink\" codetype=\"post\" entryid=\"2152\"></p>','','ADMIN','1423634426.99',NULL,NULL,1),(1889,'新婚夜就要跪键盘了','<p> <span style=\"font: 18px/28.78px 宋体; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">婚礼上，气氛正高着，主持人问新郎：“你会不会爱新娘一辈子？”</span><br style=\"font: 18px/28.78px 宋体; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: currentColor; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><span style=\"font: 18px/28.78px 宋体; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">　　新郎兴高采烈的喊：“会”。</span><br style=\"font: 18px/28.78px 宋体; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: currentColor; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><span style=\"font: 18px/28.78px 宋体; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">　　主持人：“你会不会在新娘容颜憔悴，疾病缠身的时候离开她？”</span><br style=\"font: 18px/28.78px 宋体; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: currentColor; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><span style=\"font: 18px/28.78px 宋体; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">　　猴急的新郎兴高采烈的喊：“会！”</span></p><p style=\"display:none;\" class=\"cloudreamHelperLink\" codetype=\"post\" entryid=\"2153\"></p>','','ADMIN','1423634427.27',NULL,NULL,1),(1890,'悟空与唐僧又闹笑话了','<p> </p><p style=\"font: 16px/30px Simsun; margin: 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">1.悟空：师傅，你嘴里念的是什么啊？我看你一连念好长时间了。<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">唐僧：我试试把紧箍咒倒过来念有什么效果。<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">悟空：天啊，难怪今天我的脚疼的厉害。</p><p style=\"font: 16px/30px Simsun; margin: 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">2.唐僧：“悟空，妖怪来了，去吧，战斗吧，为了理想，为了正义，为了光明，去吧，放心的去吧，不要怕前方苦难重重，危险万分，不要怕敌人阴险毒辣，诡计百出，为师已经替你买了保险，而受益人，就是我。”</p><p></p><p style=\"display:none;\" class=\"cloudreamHelperLink\" codetype=\"post\" entryid=\"2154\"></p>','','ADMIN','1423634427.53',NULL,NULL,1),(1891,'后来才觉得哪里不对','<p> <span style=\"font: 18px/28.78px 宋体; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">昨天上班和一女同事聊天，聊到求婚戒指。</span><br style=\"font: 18px/28.78px 宋体; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: currentColor; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><span style=\"font: 18px/28.78px 宋体; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">　　她说上个月他老公给她买的戒指掉到马桶里，想进了办法都没有捞出来，最后还是她老公用一块吸铁石给捞上来的。</span><br style=\"font: 18px/28.78px 宋体; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: currentColor; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: norm