ing: 0px; font-family: Verdana;\">丈夫：当然不给我妈吃了(也不给你，我自己吃)</span></p><p style=\"font: 16px/30px Simsun; margin: 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Verdana;\">妻子：我白吗？</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Verdana;\">丈夫；白，你掉到煤堆里一眼就能被认出来，真的(因为你比煤还黑)</span></p><p style=\"font: 16px/30px Simsun; margin: 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Verdana;\">妻子：我现在是不是胖了？</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Verdana;\">丈夫：那有的是呀！你很苗条。(只有骨感，没有美感。)</span></p><p style=\"font: 16px/30px Simsun; margin: 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Verdana;\">妻子：假如现在有个男人很热情地追求我，你会怎么？</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Verdana;\">丈夫脸色大变：谁？告诉我是谁？(我得好好感谢他一番，再请他吃一顿饭，然后把你好好妆扮一下就送过去。)</span></p><p style=\"font: 16px/30px Simsun; margin: 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Verdana;\">妻子：瞧！你紧张什么呀！我在逗你呢！</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Verdana;\">丈夫低头不语。</span></p><p style=\"font: 16px/30px Simsun; margin: 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Verdana;\">妻子：怎么，生气了？小傻瓜！</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Verdana;\">丈夫：对！我生气了(为什么这不是真的)</span></p><p style=\"font: 16px/30px Simsun; margin: 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Verdana;\">妻子：假如有一天我们坐上豪华轮行驶在海上，你会象杰克抱着露丝那样，扶着我在船头飞吗？</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Verdana;\">丈夫：我肯定会(毫不犹豫地把你从船头踹下去)</span></p><p style=\"font: 16px/30px Simsun; margin: 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spaci