l; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;>听完后，颇多感触，回到寝室，果断把需要背的单词改成了qq密码，</span></p><p style=font: 15px/28px \"Microsoft YaHei\", 微软雅黑; margin: 6px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;> </p><p><span style=font: 15px/28px \"Microsoft YaHei\", 微软雅黑; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;>结果，第二天醒来qq上不去了…</span></p><p></p><p style=\"display:none;\" class=\"cloudreamHelperLink\" codetype=\"post\" entryid=\"2226\"></p>','','ADMIN','1423634454.26',NULL,NULL,1),(1976,'老爸你也太可爱了','<p><span style=\"font: 18px/28.78px 宋体; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">　听麻麻讲的。那年代结婚是租个后面拉东西的货车，拉嫁妆用的，我爸去姥姥家，几个人唰唰的把嫁妆装好以后，我爸大手一挥，走！姥姥拦住了，说，媳妇儿不要啦？脑补一下当时的场景，老爸太可爱了。</span></p><p style=\"display:none;\" class=\"cloudreamHelperLink\" codetype=\"post\" entryid=\"2242\"></p>','','ADMIN','1423634454.46',NULL,NULL,1),(1977,'夫妻房事的爆笑笑话','<p> <span style=\"font: 16px/30px Simsun; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">有对夫妇非常恩爱，几乎一个月有三十天在\"行房\"。<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\"> </span></span><br style=\"font: 16px/30px Simsun; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><span style=\"font: 16px/30px Simsun; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">有一天，太太身体忽然觉得不舒服，结果医生检查之后说：你是纵欲过度导致经神性疼痛，你必须停止行房三个月，否则可能会有生命危险。<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\"> </span></span><br style=\"font: 16px/30px Simsun; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><span style=\"font: 16px/30px Simsun; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">回去后，太太把事情告诉先生，于是两人只好忍耐三个月了而分房睡了。<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\"> </span></span><br style=\"font: 16px/30px Simsun; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><span style=\"font: 16px/30px Simsun; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">可是，才刚过一星期，当晚先生就忍不住而走到太太的房间，恰好看见太太也要出房，太太看见先生很惊讶的问：有事吗？？<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\"> </span></span><br style=\"font: 16px/30px Simsun; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><span style=\"font: 16px/30px Simsun; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">先生很正经的说：\"我是来杀你的，那你呢？\"<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\"> </span></span><br style=\"font: 16px/30px Simsun; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><span style=\"font: 16px/30px Simsun; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">太太很害羞的回答：\"我是来自杀的\"</span></p><p style=\"display:none;\" class=\"cloudreamHelperLink\" codetype=\"post\" entryid=\"2235\"></p>','','ADMIN','1423634454.59',NULL,NULL,1),(1978,'哥们你也太着急了吧','<p> <span style=\"font: 18px/28.78px 宋体; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">前两天我那一对2货高中同学结婚，仪式正在进行，司仪唾沫横飞的讲着些废话，说到动情处，突然讲到，请新郎把手放在胸前，看着你美丽的新娘，谁也没想到，我那2货同学毫不犹豫的把手放在了新娘的胸上，众目睽睽啊，我们台下的快笑疯了</span>.</p><p style=\"display:none;\" class=\"cloudreamHelperLink\" codetype=\"post\" entryid=\"2243\"></p>','','ADMIN','1423634454.69',NULL,NULL,1),(1979,'孩子你赢了','<p> <span style=\"font: 18px/28.78px 宋体; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">　昨天去雪糕批发点拿货的时候，来个小萝莉，买一个雪糕，老板说5元，那个萝莉给了4元，老板说钱不够，小萝莉指着价目表对老板说：“你这不写着4元吗？”老板说：“那是批发价！”GC来了，小萝莉说：“我也是批发啊，一口气就买一个，又不是买你半个。”老板晕倒了...</span></p><p style=\"display:none;\" class=\"cloudreamHelperLink\" codetype=\"post\" entryid=\"2244\"></p>','','ADMIN','1423634454.87',NULL,NULL,1),(1980,'上帝和神父','<p> </p><p> 1.一位能言善道的神父在教堂内歌颂造物主的伟大。末了，他向在场的信徒们发问：“你们有谁敢说天下有哪件事物不是造物主最完美的杰作？”<br> 神父静待回音。突然，有位驼背的信徒自教堂的一角缓缓站起来向神父请教：“依您看，我这个驼背怎么样？”<br> 神父不假思索地告诉他：“那是我见过驼得最完美的一个背，不论在曲线或造形方面，都堪称是上帝最完美的杰作。”</p><p> 2.一个懒惰的厨子，连续几天都把剩菜热一热就端到桌子上。神父并不作声，坐下就吃。厨子很奇怪，问他为什么不先祈祷就吃饭。神父淡然回答：“桌上的每样菜，我都至少谢过两次了。”</p><p> 3.四个年轻的修女在星期五央求神父，让她们有个周末的假期，她们花了好长时间，好不容易才说服了神父，但神父要求她们在星期一的早上要诚实地告诉他她们如何度过这个周末假期。<br>到了星期一的上午，四个修女回来并轮流向神父报告。<br> 第一个修女对神父说：“原谅我，神父，我有罪……”“你做了什么”神父问。第一个修女回答：“我看了一部三级电影。”神父抬头看着天空想了几秒钟，说：“好吧，原谅你了，去喝点圣水吧！”第一个修女离开时，神父发现第四个修女抿着嘴偷偷的在笑。<br> 轮到第二个修女，她对神父说：“原谅我，神父，我有罪……”神父说：“好吧，告诉我发生了什么事？”第二个修女说：“昨晚我偷开了我哥的车子并压死了一条狗…”神父又抬头望着天空，想了近一分钟，说：“原谅你了，去喝点圣水吧。”第二个修女离开时，第四个修女笑得更大声了。<br> 接着又轮到第三个修女报告：“原谅我，神父，我有罪……”神父说：“好吧，告诉我你做了什么。”第三个修女说：“昨夜我在街上裸奔…”神父又抬头望着天空，考虑了近五分钟后，说：“上帝原谅你了，也去喝点圣水吧。”第三个修女离开时，第四个修女竟笑倒在地上，连眼泪都笑出来了……<br> 神父实在忍不住了，于是主动问第四个修女，“好吧，现在你该告诉我，这个周末发生了什么有趣的事儿让你笑成这个样子？”<br> 她好不容易忍住笑回答说：“昨晚，我在圣水里面撒了尿……”</p><p></p><p style=\"display:none;\" class=\"cloudreamHelperLink\" codetype=\"post\" entryid=\"2246\"></p>','','ADMIN','1423634455.07',NULL,NULL,1),(1981,'孩子入戏太深','<p>         <span style=\"font: 18px/28.78px 宋体; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">尼玛。。。这战争片看的。。。刚回到家，儿子居然给我来了一句：站住，你是哪个部分的。。。</span><br style=\"font: 18px/28.78px 宋体; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: currentColor; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><span style=\"font: 18px/28.78px 宋体; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">　　我说了一句：我是你老子！</span><br style=\"font: 18px/28.78px 宋体; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: currentColor; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><span style=\"font: 18px/28.78px 宋体; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">　　儿子说：狗汉奸，不要和我拉关系！</span></p><p style=\"display:none;\" class=\"cloudreamHelperLink\" codetype=\"post\" entryid=\"2247\"></p>','','ADMIN','1423634455.26',NULL,NULL,1),(1982,'爸爸的真相','<p>         <span style=\"font: 18px/28.78px 宋体; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">爸爸去哪儿的车辆赞助是英菲尼迪，爸爸回来了的车辆赞助是宝骏</span><br style=\"font: 18px/28.78px 宋体; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: currentColor; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><span style=\"font: 18px/28.78px 宋体; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">　　档次差这么多，感觉是爸爸先去赌球，输钱回来了</span></p><p style=\"display:none;\" class=\"cloudreamHelperLink\" codetype=\"post\" entryid=\"2248\"></p>','','ADMIN','1423634455.44',NULL,NULL,1),(1983,'明显在坑孩子','<p>         <span style=\"font: 18px/28.78px 宋体; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">最近四位大学同学相继当爹，生的还都是男孩。</span><br style=\"font: 18px/28.78px 宋体; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: currentColor; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><span style=\"font: 18px/28.78px 宋体; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">　　其中一哥们儿在同学群里大声疾呼：“还没生娃的同学们，你们可要生女儿啊，不然我们的儿子找不到媳妇。”</span><br style=\"font: 18px/28.78px 宋体; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: currentColor; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><span style=\"font: 18px/28.78px 宋体; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">　　一女同学淡定地回复：“没事，他们可以搞基。”</span><br style=\"font: 18px/28.78px 宋体; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: currentColor; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><span style=\"font: 18px/28.78px 宋体; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">　　群里立马响起了一片热烈的掌声。</span></p><p style=\"display:none;\" class=\"cloudreamHelperLink\" codetype=\"post\" entryid=\"2249\"></p>','','ADMIN','1423634455.63',NULL,NULL,1),(1984,'臣妾受不了啦','<p> <span style=\"font: 16px/25px 宋体, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">1、“皇上，臣妾有一事相求！恳请皇上将臣妾打入冷宫，</span><br style=\"font: 16px/25px 宋体, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><span style=\"font: 16px/25px 宋体, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">臣妾受不了了，这天气太热了！”</span></p><p style=\"font: 16px/25px 宋体, Tahoma, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 20px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; word-wrap: break-word; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">2、富二代开奔驰跑车超速行驶，被女交警当场拦住，要给开罚单。<br>富二代：“你知道我爸是谁吗？”<br>女交警：“这个得问你妈！”</p><p style=\"font: 16px/25px 宋体, Tahoma, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 20px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; word-wrap: break-word; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">3、姑娘抱怨道：“那人昨天还对我有说有笑，今天就翻脸不认人了！”<br>朋友劝姑娘：“哎，想开点吧，现在的人都很现实的。”<br>姑娘问：“那你能告诉我，人都为什么这么现实吗？”<br>朋友想了想说：“好啊，你给我一百块钱我就告诉你。”</p><p style=\"font: 16px/25px 宋体, Tahoma, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 20px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; word-wrap: break-word; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">4、从小到大，你经历过最刻骨民心的谎言是？</p><p style=\"font: 16px/25px 宋体, Tahoma, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 20px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; word-wrap: break-word; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">5、我大步走进店铺，拍着收银台，对老板大喊：<br>“我要你们店里最贵的东西！”<br>每次去一元店就是这么霸气。</p><p style=\"font: 16px/25px 宋体, Tahoma, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 20px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; word-wrap: break-word; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">6、姐姐发了一条朋友圈，内容大概是这样的：<br>“买了一大袋鸭锁骨，吃着吃着突然就哭了，<br>连鸭子都有锁骨了，我却没有……没有……”</p><p style=\"font: 16px/25px 宋体, Tahoma, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 20px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; word-wrap: break-word; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">7、男人真心不能当车模。</p><p><span style=\"font: 16px/25px 宋体, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">8、女儿一岁多，老婆喂她吃饭，女儿总是东张西望扭来动去不乖乖吃饭。</span><br style=\"font: 16px/25px 宋体, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><span style=\"font: 16px/25px 宋体, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">我一拍桌子指着女儿大吼一声：“再不好好吃，干脆就别吃了！”</span><br style=\"font: 16px/25px 宋体, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><span style=\"font: 16px/25px 宋体, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">岳母见状批评我说：“别对女儿这么凶，一点不像当爸爸的人。”<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\"> </span></span><br style=\"font: 16px/25px 宋体, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><span style=\"font: 16px/25px 宋体, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">我义正严词地说道：“我老婆喂别人的老婆吃饭，她还不好好吃，</span><br style=\"font: 16px/25px 宋体, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><span style=\"font: 16px/25px 宋体, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">弄得我老婆顿顿吃冷饭，我能不发火？！”<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\"> </span></span><br style=\"font: 16px/25px 宋体, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><span style=\"font: 16px/25px 宋体, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">岳母和老婆的眼睛里流露出感动的神彩，我的家庭地位瞬间跃升…</span></p><p style=\"display:none;\" class=\"cloudreamHelperLink\" codetype=\"post\" entryid=\"2250\"></p>','','ADMIN','1423634455.79',NULL,NULL,1),(1985,'女神你想多了','<p>         <span style=\"font: 18px/28.78px 宋体; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">载女神出去玩，走到一个荒无人烟的地方，女神:我...我想尿尿，我:这里没有厕所呀。</span><br style=\"font: 18px/28.78px 宋体; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: currentColor; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><span style=\"font: 18px/28.78px 宋体; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">　　女神:你想办法，快！</span><br style=\"font: 18px/28.78px 宋体; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: currentColor; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><span style=\"font: 18px/28.78px 宋体; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">　　我:要不这样吧，我把车停下，你去车后面尿，我不下车，这里又没有别人。</span><br style=\"font: 18px/28.78px 宋体; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: currentColor; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><span style=\"font: 18px/28.78px 宋体; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">　　啪，我的脸。</span><br style=\"font: 18px/28.78px 宋体; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: currentColor; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><span style=\"font: 18px/28.78px 宋体; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">　　女神:你个流氓，别以为我不看段子，你是想用倒车影像偷看吧？</span><br style=\"font: 18px/28.78px 宋体; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: currentColor; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><span style=\"font: 18px/28.78px 宋体; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">　　我:我一个破电动三轮，连倒档都没有，哪有倒车影像？</span></p><p style=\"display:none;\" class=\"cloudreamHelperLink\" codetype=\"post\" entryid=\"2251\"></p>','','ADMIN','1423634456.01',NULL,NULL,1),(1986,'爆笑笑话 你患了女人的常见病~已抽搐哈哈！','<p> </p><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">1、“你要男方出多少钱才肯出嫁？”</div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">“一千元。”</div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">“这么简单？你早说出来现在就不至于做剩女了。”</div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">“保持每一天都给，节假日另算。”</div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"> </div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">2、一只小苍蝇不小心撞上蜘蛛网，蜘蛛赶紧过来吐丝将其包住，准备做顿美餐，不料这时飞来了一只超大型的苍蝇，厉声喝道：“小蜘蛛，你在对我儿子做什么？”</div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">蜘蛛吓了一跳，一看大苍蝇就要将其蛛网打破，赶紧把小苍蝇送上：“你别乱来，我是看你儿子大冷天的也没穿衣服，就给他织了件毛衣保保暖。”</div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"> </div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">3、祝愿老婆大人皮肤好比黎巴嫩，秘乳有如喀麦隆，体香赛过芬兰，创意不断朝鲜，事业超过匈牙利，好运天天卢旺达，幸福不断加拿大。</div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"> </div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">4、贾宝玉：“我一碰四书五经，就觉得头痛。”</div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">林黛玉：“那你患了女人的常见病。”</div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">贾宝玉：“什么意思呀？”</div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">林黛玉：“痛经。”</div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"> </div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">5、儿子飞奔家中向父亲报喜：“爸，这次数学统考我得了100分，你准备给我奖什么？”</div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">父亲抱起儿子，“老爸要奖励你一个大大的香吻。”说罢在儿子脸上狠狠一吻。</div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">儿子十分委屈，抱怨道：“切，没一点实际的，奖什么香吻呀，臭死了。”</div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">父亲得意地笑道：“这可是正宗的香吻，有烟香又有酒香，是不是还能闻到一股浓浓的蒜香呢？哈哈哈。”</div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"> </div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">6、男孩给女孩发短信：“蓝蓝的天上白云飘，青青的草上好睡觉，心底里开花脸庞上笑，想你的感觉真美好！”</div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">女孩给男孩回复短信：“花开枝头一朵朵，谁在偷偷思念我，春风阵阵带雨过，好花必定结好果。八戒，你出栏了，在哪块草地做美梦呢？”</div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">男孩短信答复：“讨厌两个字，我只说一次，偏偏要用微笑来表示。如果非要我多说一次——格老子。我在街心公园等你呢。”</div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"> </div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">7、小明问妈妈：妈妈，今天晚上圣诞老人会到我家来吗？</div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">妈妈说道：孩子，圣诞老人肯定会来给你送礼物的！</div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">小明想了一下郑重地对妈妈说道：妈妈，圣诞老人来的时候，麻烦你告诉他一下不要从烟囱进来！</div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">妈妈不解：为什么啊小明？</div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">小明立刻说道：妈妈，难道你忘了，我们家装了抽油烟机了吗？</div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"> </div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">8、一丈夫出差很长时间回家。他很担心妻子有外遇。于是，他悄悄地问小区门卫有没有陌生男人找他老婆。</div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">门卫考虑了一下说道：先生，据我所知没有陌生男子去找你妻子。</div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">丈夫放心的点了点头。这时，门卫又说道：去你家找你老婆的都是熟人。。</div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"> </div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">9、师把成绩倒数第一的小明叫到了办公室，语重心长地说道：小明，期末考试快要到了，你准备好了吗？小明立刻自信满满地说道：老师，我准备好了。</div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">老师笑道：很好！你都是怎么准备的啊？</div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">小明说道：我们每天都锻炼身体！</div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">老师郁闷：锻炼身体做什么？</div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">小明说道：因为我爸爸说，这次还是考不好的话，就好好教训我一顿。</div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">老师吃惊之际，小明把手捏得啪啪响说道：不过，这一次，我想让爸爸知道，到底是谁教训谁！</div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"> </div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">10、书记、乡长、办公室主任、秘书四人打麻将，每次都是秘书赢钱。</div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">办公室主任问秘书，“每次打牌你稳赢，有什么诀窍？教教我。”</div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">“没有，没有，纯粹运气！”</div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">“兄弟！告诉我没关系，我请你喝酒，而且肯定不告诉别人！”办公室主任又是诱惑又是发誓。</div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">“真地？”</div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">“那肯定！”</div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">“我告诉你，书记是麻子，乡长是瘸子。两人尿不到一个壶里。他们打牌时，你没发现吗？书记不听牌也要打七饼，并说是‘拐子’，而乡长每次必打九饼，说是‘麻子’。你听牌时，什么都不要听，就听这两张，稳成牌！”</div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"> </div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">11、男友：听说你手机坏了，这是我给你买的新手机，作为生日礼物！</div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">女友：亲爱的，你最好了.... </div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">女友：亲爱的，你买套了吗？ </div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">男友：我就喜欢你这种豪爽的妹纸！你等会儿我去去就回来.....</div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">五分钟后</div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">男友：买了盒杜蕾斯，给..... </div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">女友：老娘说的是手机套！！！！</div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"> </div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">12、在清宫里头，曾经有一位娘娘独创了一种腔调，颇受大家的欢迎，也广为流传，并流传至今，尤其是广大的乡村妇女阶层，尤为热衷，这种强调不是京剧，不是徽剧，也不是昆腔，让我们用一个通俗易懂的名词来介绍：娘娘腔</div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"> </div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">13、有一位病人刚从医生那取了一大瓶药，发现药的保质期只有4天了，便跑到医生那里询问。</div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">医生微笑的对着病人说：“我知道，但是如果你按时按量服用的话，在3天之内就可以吃完了，不用担心。”</div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"> </div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">14、我们数字在数学岗位上做贡献，可是，我八字的待遇最差。</div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">在与七字的竞争中，人们希望七字胜利，巴不得八字输了，常说七胜八败。</div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">总是喜欢把八字与坏分子联系起来，乌龟下蛋硬要说是王八蛋，而倒霉鬼也说倒了八辈子霉。</div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">很难看的姿态要八字表演，走八字脚给人看，纯心让我出丑。</div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">希望渺茫的事由八字告诉人，八字没一撇，人们欺负八字太简单了。</div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">无聊的事也用八字表达，大家都很爱八卦，随意取乐八字。</div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">丑陋的面容是让大家责怪，人还是不忘让八字丢面子，丑八怪才刚好。</div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"> </div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">15、允许的坏行为</div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">抄：抄是普遍反对的行为，可是，抄底就是值得肯定的大胆行为。</div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">偷：偷是道德法律禁止的行为，可是，偷光千百来被传为佳话。</div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">砍：砍是伤害的暴力行动，理应被制止，可是，砍价却是消费者的必修课。</div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">杀：杀是牺牲生命的罪恶行径，杀人尝命，可是，网购就经常上演秒杀。</div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">抢：抢是破坏秩序得到想要的东西，为人们所不齿，可是，抢时间却无人管束。</div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"> </div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">16、老虎和狮子聊天 这个时候狐狸经过看到老虎和狮子情绪低落就问 ：</div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">两位大哥都兽王之王为何闷闷不乐？ </div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">老虎就回答我郁闷啊，我家有个母老虎。</div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">狮子就抢答我家有个河东师。</div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">跟着老虎和狮子报头疼哭。</div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">突然狐狸也哭了。</div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">老虎和狮子就问老兄你哭啥？</div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">狐狸答我家有个狐狸精!</div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"> </div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">17、刚就业时，我的首任上司说我能力不错，某某某还不如我。于是我傻傻地努力奋斗N年。</div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">当我心灰意冷时，第二任上司对我说，以后某个位子就是我的。于是又拼命干了N年。</div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">还没坐上那个位子，第三任上司来了。他毫不客气地对我说，要是不好好干，别人会好好干的。害得我不得不心惊胆战一直干下去。</div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">情伤职场，君莫效仿！</div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"> </div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">18、一同学经常找借口向老师请假。</div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">......</div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">第一次，因朋友聚会请假，“老师，我头痛。”</div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">第二次，因食堂没吃饱生闷气请假，“老师，我肚子痛。”</div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">第三次，因邻村的棵树上长满了果子请假，“老师，我手痛。”</div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">第四次，因酷爱打篮球比赛请假，“老师，我脚痛。”</div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">......</div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">几天后，老师当着全班同学的面给他做了一首诗：“头痛不发烧，肚痛嫌饭少，手痛能爬树，脚痛能行跑。”念完后对着那同学说，“这诗怎么样？很服合你的状况。”那知那同学回答道，“诗不错，还押韵呢。”</div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"> </div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">19、手术室里的病人很怕听到这些话</div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">1.这是什么？</div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">2.哼歌：让我将你心儿摘下 试着将它慢慢融化......</div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">3.这种情况我还从来没遇到过......</div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">4.你身上怎么一股酒味？</div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">5.你来帮我弄一下，我发条短信。</div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">6.这个病人长得挺漂亮的嘛。</div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">7.你是第一次给病人做手术吧？别紧张，看你的手都抖成啥样了......</div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">8.这手术室怎么连烟灰缸都没有一个？</div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">9.你动作麻利点嘛.</div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"> </div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">20、公交车上一小偷正准备偷一妇女的钱包时，边上一孩子喊道：“妈妈，妈妈，你怎么会有三只手呀，钱包上多出了一只手！”</div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"> </div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">21、110娶了120特别兴奋，120问：“娶我你真有这么开心？”</div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">110：“那是，以后生病去医院有专车接送了啊！”</div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">120：“那我以后出门被抢劫是不是也不用报警了啊？” </div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"> </div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">22、120：“老公，你嘴巴怎么老上火呀？”</div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">110：“最近火气大！抓不住犯人！”</div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">120：“要不我们要个孩子吧！”</div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">110：“要孩子干嘛？”</div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">120：“给你降火呀！”</div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">110：“啥？孩子还能降火？”</div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">120：“是啊，我妈114说了，我和你要是生孩子的话肯定是119”</div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">110：“你妈怎么什么事都知道，我在外面有小三不会也知道吧？”</div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"> </div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">23、情人节那天，老孔给老婆买了一束玫瑰。老婆很高兴就吻了老孔一下，吃饭时老婆发现老孔的脸上有一个女人的口红印变大发雷霆，让老孔从实招来。</div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">老孔见老婆如此的健忘，笑着用手指了一下脸，示意老婆再吻他一次，就能明白口红印的出处了。</div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">谁知老婆一巴掌扇过去，气狠狠地说：“别以为我不敢，出去拈花惹草还有脸笑”</div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"> </div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">24、老妈问我：“晨晨，下午有没有事啊？”</div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">我知道老妈肯定屁事繁多，就拒绝道：下午我要找朋友玩。</div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">妈妈说：“那好，我电脑坏了，下午刚好用你的。”</div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"> </div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">25、跟老公去菜市场买菜，买得差不多了，身上还剩二块五，老公说不如再买条茄子，可是他选了好几条都超重了，我一向眼力好，随手挑了一根，刚好二块五。于是我兴奋地高举茄子，大声喊道：老公，这根茄子大小正合适耶！！</div><div style=\"font: 14px/35px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">顿时众人侧目，我当场石化。</div><p></p><p style=\"display:none;\" class=\"cloudreamHelperLink\" codetype=\"post\" entryid=\"2252\"></p>','','ADMIN','1423634456.33',NULL,NULL,1),(1987,'美女请假','<p>前天下午，手下一漂亮妹妹跟我请假： 妹妹：老大，有点私事，下午要请假 我：怎么了？有什么事情？ 妹妹：你别问了，反正有事 我靠，好拽，漂亮也不能这样啊，于是我语重心长的教导她： 上班时间突然请假是不遵守职业道德的，并不是单位不通人情，如果你不给出一个信服的理由就给你假，人人都和你一样，部门不是乱了啊 妹妹：老大，放心，不会的（补充说明，本人物流部主管，部门计划、调度、操作、搬运、仓管等等都是男性，就一个文员妹妹） 我郁闷了：你是老大我是老大？你说不会就不会啊？ 结果妹妹声音比我还大：我来那个了忘记带卫生巾了，其他人能来挖拉？ 我眼冒金星，下意识的问了句：不能在门口小超市买包么？ 妹妹曰：我只用×××的，其他不舒服 然后很拽的就出门了。</p><p><br> </p><p></p><p style=\"display:none;\" class=\"cloudreamHelperLink\" codetype=\"post\" entryid=\"2253\"></p>','','ADMIN','1423634456.55',NULL,NULL,1),(1988,'我是一位公正的法官','<p> 一位法官跟他的朋友说：“请你想像一下，我们这里营私舞弊泛滥到何等地步！前天，就在诉讼程序刚要开始，被告的辩护律师转送给我1000美元。怎么能这样呢，啊？过了一会儿，受害者的辩护律师也硬塞给我1200美元。可我不是那种在诉讼程序中昧良心偏袒一方的人。所以，为了做到公平公正，我又归还受害者200美元。”<br></p><p style=\"display:none;\" class=\"cloudreamHelperLink\" codetype=\"post\" entryid=\"2254\"></p>','','ADMIN','1423634456.73',NULL,NULL,1),(1989,'这是什么情况','<p> <span style=\"font: 18px/28.78px 宋体; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">每次坐地铁都会看到一个盲人老大爷吹着口琴，身后还跟着一个盲人老大娘，每次我都是怜悯之心涌上心头，都会给大爷5块钱，但是今天当我再次看见大爷时，发现身后的大娘居然换人了！居然换人了！什么情况？</span></p><p style=\"display:none;\" class=\"cloudreamHelperLink\" codetype=\"post\" entryid=\"2255\"></p>','','ADMIN','1423634456.92',NULL,NULL,1),(1990,'二爷保佑，我去替天行道','<p> <span style=\"font: 18px/28.78px 宋体; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">有一次跟朋友去ktv喝酒，那货喝多了，走得时候看见大厅有关二爷人像，扑通一声跪那了，说二爷保佑，我去替天行道，上去把二爷手里的关刀抗了就跑…尼玛，怎么都拦不住，最后人家ktv老板带十多个人追了两条街！</span></p><p style=\"display:none;\" class=\"cloudreamHelperLink\" codetype=\"post\" entryid=\"2256\"></p>','','ADMIN','1423634457.28',NULL,NULL,1),(1991,'朗朗上口的两幅对联','<p> <span style=\"font: 18px/28.78px 宋体; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">朗朗上口的两幅对联。㈠ 上联：no zuo no die why you try 下联：no try no high give me five 横批： let it go。㈡ 上联：no zuo no die why you cry 下联：you try you die dont ask why 横批： just do it。</span></p><p style=\"display:none;\" class=\"cloudreamHelperLink\" codetype=\"post\" entryid=\"2257\"></p>','','ADMIN','1423634457.42',NULL,NULL,1),(1992,'伤不起的理科生','<p>         <span style=\"font: 18px/28.78px 宋体; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">有人说，理科女生再淑女，一做起题来就会暴露自己的身份。</span><br style=\"font: 18px/28.78px 宋体; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: currentColor; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><span style=\"font: 18px/28.78px 宋体; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">　　习惯性的把前额的头发往上捋，露出大大的额头，因为CPU高速运作时需要良好的散热……</span></p><p style=\"display:none;\" class=\"cloudreamHelperLink\" codetype=\"post\" entryid=\"2258\"></p>','','ADMIN','1423634457.57',NULL,NULL,1),(1993,'当你女朋友不回你短信时','<p> <span style=\"font: 18px/28.78px 宋体; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">当你女朋友不回你短信时，25%的男生认为：也许她睡了吧；15%的男生认为：估计在忙吧；60%的男生认为：我CAO！我又犯什么错了？</span></p><p style=\"display:none;\" class=\"cloudreamHelperLink\" codetype=\"post\" entryid=\"2259\"></p>','','ADMIN','1423634457.71',NULL,NULL,1),(1994,'笑话经典，不看后悔哈','<p> </p><p style=\"font: 16px/25px 宋体, Tahoma, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 20px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; word-wrap: break-word; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">1、我同事家的孩子上小学。一次语文考试的成语题目是：冰( )雪( )，<br>答案大家都知道是冰天雪地，而同事家的孩子的答案把我们都笑趴了。<br>他的答案是“冰糖雪梨”。从此之后，同事再也不买饮料了！</p><p style=\"font: 16px/25px 宋体, Tahoma, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 20px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; word-wrap: break-word; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">2、笑死我了，刚和朋友出去吃早餐，<br>我说：“你为啥还不找女友？”<br>他神回复：“像我这种不帅，又没品的男生，<br>追女生不是靠自己有多努力，而是赌这女的眼有多瞎！”<br>#编想起《爱情公寓》中张伟也说过类似很霸气侧漏的话：<br>“和我赌不是看你要什么，而是看我有什么。”#</p><p style=\"font: 16px/25px 宋体, Tahoma, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 20px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; word-wrap: break-word; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">3、青年去拜见禅师问：“有没有不用劳动就能发财的诀窍呢？”<br>禅师把青年带到猪圈旁，青年恍然大悟说：<br>“你的意思是要我把这些猪偷出去卖掉，就有钱了是吗？”<br>禅师说：“我是说你是猪脑子，有这么好的事，我还会告诉你呀？”</p><p></p><p style=\"display:none;\" class=\"cloudreamHelperLink\" codetype=\"post\" entryid=\"2260\"></p>','','ADMIN','1423634457.85',NULL,NULL,1),(1995,'6个哭笑不得的鬼故事','<p>1.一家医院的加护病房的病人总是在星期天十一点左右死掉，甚至有些人那时还没有生命危险。<br>这让医生们困惑不解，有的甚至以为是某种超自然的力量在起作用，于是全世界的专家组成一个科研机构来调查事情的原因。他们迅速赶到这家医院。<br>一个星期天上午，十点前几分钟，医院里所有的医生和护士跟随专家组来到加护病房的前面，留心去看可怕现象发生。<br>时钟刚刚敲响十一点，在星期天打扫的清洁工走进加护病房，拔掉重病号的生命维持系统电线插头，然后插上了吸尘器插头，开始打扫卫生……</p><p>2.建筑师为大富商修造一座陵墓。   <br>大富商问忙了一年的建筑师：还缺什么吗？建筑师说，现在只缺你了。</p><p>3.监牢里,一位死刑犯焦躁不安.一位好心的看守对他说:“别怕,电流很强,也就一眨眼的工夫,丝毫没有痛苦的.“这时,从刑场那边传来惨叫声.“什么声音?“死刑犯战战兢兢地问.“我也不知道.“看守说着就去刑场看个究竟.“没什么,赶上停电了,只好用蜡烛.“看守回来后若无其事地说.<br>　　<br>4.有三个人到非洲探险，不小心偷看到了一位酋长的女儿在洗澡。被抓后，酋长问第一个人想死还是想被弹JJ，他当然回答说弹JJ。于是被拉下去弹JJ50下，惨叫......。又问第二个人想死还是想被弹JJ，他犹豫了一下，好死不如赖活，他也选择了弹JJ，于是被拉下去弹JJ100下，极其刺耳恐怖的惨叫，被拖回来已经奄奄一息，而且JJ好象已经完全废了。又问第三个人，想死还是想被弹JJ。他犹豫半天，看看他们两个如此痛苦，而且东西也坏了，觉得选死也许会出现奇迹，起码没有那么痛苦啊，所以就壮烈的回答说：死。于是酋长说：“拉下去，弹JJ弹到死。“<br>　　<br>5.食人族父子打猎，其子擒一瘦子，其父曰：没肉,放到湖里去打鱼虾！其子又擒一胖子，其父曰：<br>　　放，太腻,剖开晒干,冬天作皮袄！其子又擒一美女，其父曰：带回家，晚上把你妈吃了!<br>　　<br>6.一妇女在他丈夫的墓碑上写到：“终于硬了”</p><p></p><p style=\"display:none;\" class=\"cloudreamHelperLink\" codetype=\"post\" entryid=\"2245\"></p>','','ADMIN','1423634457.9',NULL,NULL,1),(1996,'联合国点名','<p> </p><p>近日，由于中东坏事频频，联合国会务频繁，众多代表偷偷缺席，故安南不得不一一点名，要代表报到：<br>安南：日本的未婚先有子和松下裤带子小姐来了没？<br>有子和带子：到！！<br>安南：有子和带子都到了，哦，那日本另一代表－－整夜折腾一次郎来了没？<br>一次郎：到！！！<br>安南：南韩的嫖娼妓来了没？<br>嫖娼妓：到！！！！<br>安南：越南的“软中硬”来了没？<br>软中硬：到！！！！！<br>安南：罗马尼亚的“扒你丝内裤”先生来了没？<br>内库：到！！！<br>安南：伊拉克的“扑你老母”先生来了没？</p><p>劳姆：到！！！！<br>安南：俄罗斯的“扎你波搞你小鸡”（扎尔波高尔晓基）先生来了没？<br>高尔晓基：到！！！<br>安南：最后，中国代表，房事勤先生来了没？<br>房事勤：到！！！！！！！！<br></p><p></p><p style=\"display:none;\" class=\"cloudreamHelperLink\" codetype=\"post\" entryid=\"2261\"></p>','','ADMIN','1423634458.0',NULL,NULL,1),(1997,'新鲜出炉的爆笑男女笑话','<p>1.新娘大叹：<br>前脚过完情人节，没想到转眼就是妇女节了.<br>新郎也大叹：<br>十二点前，还是光棍节.没想到，刚刚过了一个剩蛋节</p><p>2.一单身汉向女友求婚，遭拒绝！单身汉自卑的说：“算了，我这辈子都别想结婚了！！”女友：“大丈夫何患无妻？我拒绝你，不见得别人会拒绝你。”单身汉一声叹息：“连你这样的都不要我，你觉得还有别人要我吗？”</p><p>3.血气方刚的杨戬看上了嫦娥！<br>哮天犬劝说道：你可别想不开，嫦娥这美女，人人盯着呢，你没机会的，天篷已经被贬下界，你要引以为戒！<br>杨戬笑道：只要你肯帮忙，我就能搞上手！<br>哮天犬：我能怎么帮？<br>杨戬：天狗食月啊！到时你把月亮吞了，我搞嫦娥，谁看得见！</p><p>4.老公：“老婆，坐在你边上吃饭就是凉快！”<br>老婆：“为什么呢？”<br>老公：“瞧你那夹菜速度跟电风扇似得！”</p><p>5.女友：“亲爱的，你得多喝水啊，这样才能身体好！”<br>男友：“你怎么知道我没喝水啊？”<br>女友：“因为今天一天你都没去厕所！”<br>男友：“嘿，你又是怎么知道我没去厕所呢？”<br>女友：“因为你的裤链一直没拉上过。。。。。”<br></p><p></p><p style=\"display:none;\" class=\"cloudreamHelperLink\" codetype=\"post\" entryid=\"2262\"></p>','','ADMIN','1423634458.15',NULL,NULL,1),(1998,'大夫你看看我这是属于什么B','<p> </p><p style=\"font: 14px/30px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 10px auto 1em; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">1、某医院在做B超检查，一位男工作人员告诉大家，彩B在201室，黑白B在202室，病人们都到指定房间做检查去了，这时候有一位妇女红着脸走到工作人员跟前把裤子一脱，说道：大夫你看看我这是属于什么B？....<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">2、医院走廊里一群人在等待尿检，每人手里都端着自己的尿样。轮到一个叫王尚举的患者，护士没多想，便随口喊:王尚举！然后所有患者都把手里的尿样举高了一点，护士又喊道:王尚举！.....然后患者们又把尿样举高了一点......护士还喊:王尚举！！！然后所有患者都把尿样高高举起...这时王尚举意识到护士是在喊自己，便大声答:到！然后所有的患者都把尿样倒头上了。</p><p style=\"font: 14px/30px Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 10px auto 1em; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">3、卖油条的男人解完小手回来，不洗手就给女顾客拿油条。被女顾客察觉后说：“你拿的我不要，让你媳妇给我拿！”媳妇给她拿完油条后，看着女顾客远去的背影嘀咕道：“哼！他才摸了一下你就嫌脏，我昨晚摸了一宿……”</p><p></p><p style=\"display:none;\" class=\"cloudreamHelperLink\" codetype=\"post\" entryid=\"2263\"></p>','','ADMIN','1423634458.42',NULL,NULL,1),(1999,'从一侧笑话里领悟出来的人生大道理','<p> </p><p style=\"font: 16px/30px Simsun; margin: 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">1、有个人骑电瓶车逆行，被Pol.ice逮住，要罚款50，他立马就火了，大声呵斥Pol.ice：“不就是逆行吗，又不是汽车，还要罚我50，我要是请出我大爷来，你得倒找我50。”<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">警察也怒了：“你把你大爷叫来，我看他有多牛，我就不信还让我给你50！”<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">这货立马从兜里掏出一百元，指着毛爷爷头像说：“这就是我大爷，找我50！”</p><p style=\"font: 16px/30px Simsun; margin: 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">2、狗不能喂的太饱，人不能处的太好；忍一时得寸进尺，退一步变本加厉；<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">玩笑别太过，要不都是祸；情不够，钱来凑；<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">有钱身后一群狗，没钱社会路难走；看清对你好的，记住被谁咬的；<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">该吃吃，该喝喝，破事儿别往心里搁；<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">是人是狗，是敌是友，时间长了自己瞅；凡人只说三分话，留得七分打天下。</p><p></p><p style=\"display:none;\" class=\"cloudreamHelperLink\" codetype=\"post\" entryid=\"2264\"></p>','','ADMIN','1423634458.68',NULL,NULL,1),(2000,'活得久了，你就容易被糗被囧到','<p style=\"font: 16px/30px Simsun; margin: 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">1、一个画家拎着他的油画箱子到小山村里面写生，刚进村被几个小孩子跟着，七嘴八舌的问他是干什么的。<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">画家转起身来，打开箱子，让他们看，这时孩子们说：“哦，原来是个卖牙膏的啊。”</p><p style=\"font: 16px/30px Simsun; margin: 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">2、一位老人对他的朋友说：“我好孤独啊！在这个世界上，我除了一只小狗之外，再没有其他亲人了。”<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">朋友十分同情地说：“那你就再养一只小狗吧！”</p><p style=\"font: 16px/30px Simsun; margin: 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">3、那天逛街遇到朋友，我跟他打招呼：“好久没见面了，最近忙吗？”<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">“忙！忙的屁股直冒烟儿！”说着，嘴里吐了一个长长的大烟圈。</p><p></p><p style=\"display:none;\" class=\"cloudreamHelperLink\" codetype=\"post\" entryid=\"2265\"></p>','','ADMIN','1423634458.94',NULL,NULL,1),(2001,'搞笑幽默的方式有点歪门邪道','<p> </p><p style=\"font: 16px/30px Simsun; margin: 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">1、碗对开水说：“兄弟，别再那么花心了，对感情专一一点好不好？”<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">开水委屈的说：“天地良心啊！我对感情的态度是日月可鉴，清澈见底。你说，我哪里不专一了？”<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">碗说：“小样儿，你还真能装啊！你一会儿‘泡茶’，一会儿忙着‘泡饭’，还时不时的泡‘方便面’。你走马灯似的泡着MM，还有脸说你专一？”</p><p style=\"font: 16px/30px Simsun; margin: 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">2、狗狗恋爱了，但是它很担忧，因为它不知道对方喜不喜欢.....吃屎的男人<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">猫咪恋爱了，但是它很担忧，因为它不知道对方喜不喜欢......长胡子的女人</p><p></p><p style=\"display:none;\" class=\"cloudreamHelperLink\" codetype=\"post\" entryid=\"2266\"></p>','','ADMIN','1423634459.19',NULL,NULL,1),(2002,'机缘巧合就造就的爆笑糗事','<p> 1、下班地铁上，突然加速没站稳，碰到旁边男的了，还踩了他一脚。<br>他正低头玩手机，我非常抱歉，开口跟他说对不起，结果尼玛口香糖掉到他手机上了！！！！<br>2、一哥们去水果店买了15块钱的水果，给了100块，老板给找了95块，<br>那哥们高兴坏了，掉头就走，回宿舍哈哈大笑说那老板真是傻，找钱都会找错。<br>当我们问他买的水果在哪的时候，哥们不笑了！！<br>3、今天打一“黑车”，路遇交警拦车，交警怀疑其是黑车。<br>只见黑车司机非常老练地下车，解释道：我们是朋友，我还有她电话呢，不信我给你拨一个。<br>我电话果然响起，交警一把抢过去，上面的来电显示是：黑车司机……<br>4、一起好几个朋友一起打完台球去宵夜的路上，老公肚子疼，路上去找个厕所。<br>一朋友说：快点啊，一车人要宵夜，都等着你拉屎了。<br>5、今天去KFC排队，前面个MM不小心踩了我的脚， 我不禁后退一步，却踩了后面妹子的脚，她在玩手机。 <br>只听前面的妹子说：“对不起。”<br>后面应着：“没关系。”</p><p style=\"display:none;\" class=\"cloudreamHelperLink\" codetype=\"post\" entryid=\"2268\"></p>','','ADMIN','1423634459.46',NULL,NULL,1),(2003,'自做自受','<p> <span style=\"font: 14px/30px simsun, arial, 宋体; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">小海问小虎：“你的额头怎么肿了？”小虎说：“真倒霉，刚才我在阳台看见我爸爸和我妹妹小兰走回家，小兰走前面，我想等小兰一到家突然跑出吓她一跳，于是我就躲门背后，可没想到我爸爸突然大便急要拉大便很快跑回家，我爸爸一到家门口就很用力推开门把我的额头碰肿了！”小海边笑边说：“真好笑，你自做自受！”</span></p><p style=\"display:none;\" class=\"cloudreamHelperLink\" codetype=\"post\" entryid=\"2269\"></p>','','ADMIN','1423634459.7',NULL,NULL,1),(