是一股微弱的诙谐冷风','<p> <span style=font: 12px/18px \"sans serif\", tahoma, verdana, helvetica; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;>1、小明在路上走，看到前面有个腿脚不方便的人一瘸一拐地在走，他就在后面学，但感觉不过瘾，就跑到前面一瘸一拐地走。</span><br style=font: 12px/18px \"sans serif\", tahoma, verdana, helvetica; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;><span style=font: 12px/18px \"sans serif\", tahoma, verdana, helvetica; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;>后来，从路旁边冲出来一壮汉，把这个腿脚不方便的人打了一顿，并骂道：“别人残疾现已很不幸了你TM还学人家！”</span><br style=font: 12px/18px \"sans serif\", tahoma, verdana, helvetica; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;><span style=font: 12px/18px \"sans serif\", tahoma, verdana, helvetica; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;>2、王思聪你好，我并不知道你是谁，但看谈论你如同有点小名气。</span><br style=font: 12px/18px \"sans serif\", tahoma, verdana, helvetica; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;><span style=font: 12px/18px \"sans serif\", tahoma, verdana, helvetica; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;>我好几次都在热门谈论看到我未婚妻喊你老公，我现已摔了她手机骂了她，一起也期望你不要在缠着她。</span><br style=font: 12px/18px \"sans serif\", tahoma, verdana, helvetica; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;><span style=font: 12px/18px \"sans serif\", tahoma, verdana, helvetica; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;>我爸爸是公司老总，身价千万，假如你在缠着我未婚妻，你信不信我拿钱砸死你！！！</span><br style=font: 12px/18px \"sans serif\", tahoma, verdana, helvetica; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;><span style=font: 12px/18px \"sans serif\", tahoma, verdana, helvetica; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;>3、看到小侄女，老夫榜首句话即是：“考的如何啊？”我要把这种苦楚一代一代传承下去。 </span><br style=font: 12px/18px \"sans serif\", tahoma, verdana, helvetica; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;><span style=font: 12px/18px \"sans serif\", tahoma, verdana, helvetica; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;>小侄女答道：我和男朋友都没考好。叔叔你女朋友呢？ </span><br style=font: 12px/18px \"sans serif\", tahoma, verdana, helvetica; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;><span style=font: 12px/18px \"sans serif\", tahoma, verdana, helvetica; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;>我听完后，伸出手来轻轻地捏了一下小侄女的脸，然后微笑说：“她刚刚亲了你一下……”</span><br style=font: 12px/18px \"sans serif\", tahoma, verdana, helvetica; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;><span style=font: 12px/18px \"sans serif\", tahoma, verdana, helvetica; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;>4、早上师傅对刚收的学徒说：“出去看看今日啥风向，看看咱们能不能出海捕鱼。”</span><br style=font: 12px/18px \"sans serif\", tahoma, verdana, helvetica; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;><span style=font: 12px/18px \"sans serif\", tahoma, verdana, helvetica; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;>学徒出门一会回来提到：“怎样看法？”</span><br style=font: 12px/18px \"sans serif\", tahoma, verdana, helvetica; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;><span style=font: 12px/18px \"sans serif\", tahoma, verdana, helvetica; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;>师傅：“白痴，拿样东西抛向天空，看它落到哪，不就知道了。”</span><br style=font: 12px/18px \"sans serif\", tahoma, verdana, helvetica; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;><span style=font: 12px/18px \"sans serif\", tahoma, verdana, helvetica; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;>学徒出门找了块砖头，一会回来说：“师傅，刮的是下风。”</span></p><p style=\"display:none;\" class=\"cloudreamHelperLink\" codetype=\"post\" entryid=\"2495\"></p>','','ADMIN','1423634650.47',NULL,NULL,1),(2220,'逗B二货,怎样笑你都不为过','<p> 1、A：“昨天夜里我干了件大事，感觉立马回到了幼年。”<br>B：“啥事？”<br>A：“尿床。”<br>2、A：“你有没有恐高症？”<br>B：“有！我垂头时望脚尖，都会觉得头晕！”<br>3、火车上突闻到一股脚臭味，余光一瞟就看见我对面妹子脱了鞋，…就听到我上铺喊了句：大妹子啊。<br>那妹子‘啊’了一声。<br>上铺又说：大城市来的吧？<br>妹子说：你怎样晓得啊？<br>上铺笑道：一闻这味怎样着也是香港的啊～～<br>4、“你怎样一有钱就买包包啊？”<br>“有钱当然买包包啊。你走在路上拿着爱马仕，通过的人都晓得你有钱。你不能拉着每个人说：呵呵，姐昨夜吸了五万块的粉。关于我这种虚荣的人来说，得憋死。就跟搞了吴彦祖不让说一样，我图啥呀！”<br>5、我俩逗B哥们看动物国际来着，提到大马哈鱼为了产卵，最终付出了生命，河滩上漂着好多死鱼，这时A说：“这么多死鱼你进入捡两条回来煮呗。”<br>B：“怎样进入？”<br>A：“把电视砸了不就能够了。”<br>其时我那哥们就急了：“你TM当我傻B啊！我要是把电视砸了，那一河的水流出来还不把我家淹了啊！”</p><p style=\"display:none;\" class=\"cloudreamHelperLink\" codetype=\"post\" entryid=\"2496\"></p>','','ADMIN','1423634650.71',NULL,NULL,1),(2221,'囧到直想爆粗口啊!','<p> 1、我搭档有个习气，喜爱把硬币扔在轿车的储物盒里。有一次他开车去吃快餐，二十几块钱，吃完后发现没带钱包，他俄然想到了车里的那个储物盒。<br>他对服务员说：“我的钱忘在车里了，我去拿给你！”说着，他飞驰出了饭馆，到车里，翻开储物盒，把硬币倒出来，数了数，够了。<br>当他捧着一大把硬币回到饭馆给服务员的时分，服务员猎奇地盯着他，问：“刚上街讨的吧？”<br>2、“请问你这里的WiFi密码是？”<br>“史努比，小写的。”<br>我输入snoopy，多次失利，我置疑自个拼错了单词，怯怯地问：“对不起，能帮我写下来吗？”<br>他面带嫌弃，丢过来一张纸条，只见上面写着：shinubi.....<br>3、路上偶遇同学，问他是不是有一块钱零钱。我只要3块钱。来回坐车要4块。<br>他说这好办，你把一块钱的撕成两半就行了。<br>我一听好主意啊，那你帮我撕吧，然后我就，我就默默地掏出了3个硬币给他。。。。<br>4、酒后和一领导同住宾馆，夜里口渴起来喝水，可暖瓶满是开水，到一杯预备凉了再喝，小睡一会成果空杯，一晚重复四次居然都没喝到！<br>清晨领导笑眯眯夸奖，年轻人有出路。<br>5、“我和我妈谁更美丽？”<br>“你妈比你美丽”<br>“不想说就不说！别爆粗！”</p><p style=\"display:none;\" class=\"cloudreamHelperLink\" codetype=\"post\" entryid=\"2497\"></p>','','ADMIN','1423634650.98',NULL,NULL,1),(2222,'小老板爆出“坑爹”新技能','<p> 1、“老板你这西瓜甜吗？ ”<br>“甜的我都舍不得卖！”<br>“那给我拿一个。”<br>回家切开一尝一点也不甜，我回去找老板理论。“你怎样哄人，一点都不甜啊！”<br>“我没哄人啊，甜的我的确舍不得卖啊！”<br>2、“老板给我来条鱼。”老板敏捷抓起一条放进袋子里就称。<br>“你把水倒倒再称，我买鱼又不是买水！”<br>老板回了一句：“你娶个媳妇娘家不搭点陪嫁品啊！”<br>3、看到饭馆的wifi暗码是zlygdsx，感受很奇怪就问服务员：“你家暗码怎样这么难记啊？”<br>服务员笑着说：“不难记。是再来一个地三鲜。”<br>我一边读一边输入暗码，于是服务员帮我点了一个地三鲜。<br>4、在街上看到一家卖皮带的，大条幅上写着‘不是真皮假一赔十’，就买了一条，回家后发现不是真皮的，就回去找商家，结果他说，这不是写的很明白吗：不是真皮，假一赔十！<br>不坑不骗的，假如你在我这买到真皮的，我立马陪你十条！我们经商的考究的就是一个真实！<br>我竟无言以对…</p><p style=\"display:none;\" class=\"cloudreamHelperLink\" codetype=\"post\" entryid=\"2498\"></p>','','ADMIN','1423634651.2',NULL,NULL,1),(2223,'伤者的儿子','<p> <span style=font: 15px/28px \"Microsoft YaHei\", 微软雅黑; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;>某一天发生交通意外，一名记者想进去看看。不过他挤了好长时间也没进去，这时，记者想出了一个办法，他就大声喊道：“请你们让开，我是伤者的儿子。”一旁的人果然让开了，记者说：“还是我这办法管用。”</span></p><p style=font: 15px/28px \"Microsoft YaHei\", 微软雅黑; margin: 6px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;> <span style=font: 15px/28px \"Microsoft YaHei\", 微软雅黑; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;>进去一看，原来伤者是一头猪......</span></p><p></p><p style=\"display:none;\" class=\"cloudreamHelperLink\" codetype=\"post\" entryid=\"2499\"></p>','','ADMIN','1423634651.44',NULL,NULL,1),(2224,'你却是想吸，TM你吸得起吗','<p><span style=\"font: 18px/28.78px 宋体; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">    甲：吸毒太可怕了啊，又进去俩。</span><br style=\"font: 18px/28.78px 宋体; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: currentColor; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><span style=\"font: 18px/28.78px 宋体; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">　　乙：是啊。</span><br style=\"font: 18px/28.78px 宋体; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: currentColor; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><span style=\"font: 18px/28.78px 宋体; text-align: left; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 