; PADDING-TOP: 0px\">一个瘸了腿的青年卖唱的，把一个要饭的聋哑老人地盘给占了...，两人僵持半天...老人抢不过年轻的呀...在旁边生气...<br>然后青年拿起麦试试：“喂，喂，”两声响！老人直接被震迷糊了，口吐白沫...吓的青年撒腿就跑！连闯两个红灯，头都没回...”<br></p></a></p><p><a style=\"PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; DISPLAY: block; FONT: medium/24px microsoft yahei, Hiragino Sans GB, Hiragino Sans GB W3; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; COLOR: rgb(68,68,68); WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-DECORATION: none; PADDING-TOP: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" class=\"image share_url\" target=\"_blank\"><p style=\"PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px\">老人从地上起来：“还敢跟老子跟抢地盘！”<br>围观的都给俩骗子点了个赞...</p></a></p><p style=\"display:none;\" class=\"cloudreamHelperLink\" codetype=\"post\" entryid=\"2664\"></p>','','ADMIN','1423634807.37',NULL,NULL,1),(2388,'一件裙子的故事','<a style=\"PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; DISPLAY: block; FONT: medium/24px microsoft yahei, Hiragino Sans GB, Hiragino Sans GB W3; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; COLOR: rgb(68,68,68); WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-DECORATION: none; PADDING-TOP: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" class=\"image share_url\" title=\"下一条\" href=\"http://www.neihanshequ.com/p3538706586/\" se_prerender_url=\"complete\"><p> <a style=\"PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; DISPLAY: block; FONT: medium/24px microsoft yahei, Hiragino Sans GB, Hiragino Sans GB W3; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; COLOR: rgb(68,68,68); WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-DECORATION: none; PADDING-TOP: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" class=\"image share_url\" title=\"下一条\" href=\"http://www.neihanshequ.com/p3538706586/\" se_prerender_url=\"complete\"></a></p></a><p style=\"PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px\"></p><p style=\"PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px\">女生A：听说你买了条新裙子？</p><p style=\"PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px\">女生B：别提了。</p><p style=\"PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px\">女生A：怎么了？</p><p style=\"PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px\">女生B：我在地摊上花30元买了条裙子，后来觉得太露了，就花190元买了个蕾丝小披肩。可是发型不搭呀，于是花450元烫了个头发。</p><p style=\"PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px\">女生A：真奢侈，不过我能理解。</p><p style=\"PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px\">女生B：后来为了搭配，我又买了几件小首饰，花了2000元。</p><p style=\"PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px\">女生A：这回完美了。</p><p style=\"PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px\">女生B：倒是完美了，可第二天我把新裙子洗完后晾在外面，下班回来发现，裙子被风吹跑，找不到了……</p><a style=\"PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; DISPLAY: block; FONT: medium/24px microsoft yahei, Hiragino Sans GB, Hiragino Sans GB W3; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; COLOR: rgb(68,68,68); WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-DECORATION: none; PADDING-TOP: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" class=\"image share_url\" title=\"下一条\" href=\"http://www.neihanshequ.com/p3538706586/\" se_prerender_url=\"complete\"><p style=\"PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px\"></p></a><p></p><p style=\"display:none;\" class=\"cloudreamHelperLink\" codetype=\"post\" entryid=\"2665\"></p>','','ADMIN','1423634807.6',NULL,NULL,1),(2389,'穷玩车，富玩表，屌丝玩手机，二逼拼电脑。','<p> <a style=\"PADDING-BOTT