0px\">住校，晚上天气闷热，又没有电，于是把凉席铺到楼道睡。刚躺下就被蚊子编队围住…翻箱倒柜找出盘蚊香，点上放在脚底下，这才安然睡去…又不到一个钟头，我被一声男人的尖叫惊醒，我大怒，只见一人影哆哆嗦嗦地说：“你...你大爷的！铺个草席躺楼道里就够吓人的了，还烧柱香…”</span></p><p style=\"display:none;\" class=\"cloudreamHelperLink\" codetype=\"post\" entryid=\"2693\"></p>','','ADMIN','1423634814.59',NULL,NULL,1),(2417,'同行','<p> <span style=\"TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; DISPLAY: inline !important; FONT: 14px/24px 微软雅黑; WHITE-SPACE: normal; FLOAT: none; LETTER-SPACING: normal; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); WORD-SPACING: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">警察抓了一算命先生，正在审问。　</span><br style=\"TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; FONT: 14px/24px 微软雅黑; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); WORD-SPACING: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; DISPLAY: inline !important; FONT: 14px/24px 微软雅黑; WHITE-SPACE: normal; FLOAT: none; LETTER-SPACING: normal; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); WORD-SPACING: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">　　警察：腐朽的、封建的、伪科学、意淫的东西你自己信吗？　</span><br style=\"TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; FONT: 14px/24px 微软雅黑; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); WORD-SPACING: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; DISPLAY: inline !important; FONT: 14px/24px 微软雅黑; WHITE-SPACE: normal; FLOAT: none; LETTER-SPACING: normal; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); WORD-SPACING: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">　　算命先生：不信。</span><br style=\"TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; FONT: 14px/24px 微软雅黑; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); WORD-SPACING: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; DISPLAY: inline !important; FONT: 14px/24px 微软雅黑; WHITE-SPACE: normal; FLOAT: none; LETTER-SPACING: normal; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); WORD-SPACING: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">　　警察：那为什么还要宣传给别人信？</span><br style=\"TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; FONT: 14px/24px 微软雅黑; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); WORD-SPACING: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; DISPLAY: inline !important; FONT: 14px/24px 微软雅黑; WHITE-SPACE: normal; FLOAT: none; LETTER-SPACING: normal; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); WORD-SPACING: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">　　算命先生：为了骗钱啊，混口饭吃。</span><br style=\"TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; FONT: 14px/24px 微软雅黑; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); WORD-SPACING: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; DISPLAY: inline !important; FONT: 14px/24px 微软雅黑; WHITE-SPACE: normal; FLOAT: none; LETTER-SPACING: normal; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); WORD-SPACING: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">　　警察：骗钱？罚款1千元。</span><br style=\"TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; FONT: 14px/24px 微软雅黑; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); WORD-SPACING: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; DISPLAY: inline !important; FONT: 14px/24px 微软雅黑; WHITE-SPACE: normal; FLOAT: none; LETTER-SPACING: normal; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); WORD-SPACING: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">　　算命先生：同志，都是同行，下手咋这么狠呢？　</span><br style=\"TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; FONT: 14px/24px 微软雅黑; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); WORD-SPACING: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; DISPLAY: inline !important; FONT: 14px/24px 微软雅黑; WHITE-SPACE: normal; FLOAT: none; LETTER-SPACING: normal; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); WORD-SPACING: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">　　警察：嗨，小样，别跟我套近乎，谁跟你是同行？</span><br style=\"TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; FONT: 14px/24px 微软雅黑; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); WORD-SPACING: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; DISPLAY: inline !important; FONT: 14px/24px 微软雅黑; WHITE-SPACE: normal; FLOAT: none; LETTER-SPACING: normal; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); WORD-SPACING: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">　　算命先生：你们整日宣传共产主义，难道你们自己真的相信？还不都是为了骗钱吗？</span></p><p style=\"display:none;\" class=\"cloudreamHelperLink\" codetype=\"post\" entryid=\"2694\"></p>','','ADMIN','1423634814.87',NULL,NULL,1),(2418,'一样？','<p> <span style=\"TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; DISPLAY: inline !important; FONT: 12px/18px sans serif, tahoma, verdana, helvetica; WHITE-SPACE: normal; FLOAT: none; LETTER-SPACING: normal; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); WORD-SPACING: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">我有一个爱喝酒的哥们，整日吃喝嫖赌，浪费着自己的青春和身体。</span><br style=\"TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; FONT: 12px/18px sans serif, tahoma, verdana, helvetica; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); WORD-SPACING: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; DISPLAY: inline !important; FONT: 12px/18px sans serif, tahoma, verdana, helvetica; WHITE-SPACE: normal; FLOAT: none; LETTER-SPACING: normal; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); WORD-SPACING: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">　　有一次跟我一块喝酒。我劝他：伙计，别喝那么多酒了，干点正事吧，要不身体很快就垮了。你看看我邻居，天天拿出2个小时来锻炼，身体倍棒，吃嘛嘛香。</span></p><p><span style=\"TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; DISPLAY: inline !important; FONT: 12px/18px sans serif, tahoma, verdana, helvetica; WHITE-SPACE: normal; FLOAT: none; LETTER-SPACING: normal; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); WORD-SPACING: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">　　那哥们一听，咽下了嘴里的啤酒，回答道：嗨，这有什么好羡慕的？你那邻居天天锻炼，比我能多活5年，但这五年时光都浪费在锻炼上了，还不是一样？</span><br style=\"TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; FONT: 12px/18px sans serif, tahoma, verdana, helvetica; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); WORD-SPACING: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"></p><p style=\"display:none;\" class=\"cloudreamHelperLink\" codetype=\"post\" entryid=\"2695\"></p>','','ADMIN','1423634815.16',NULL,NULL,1),(2419,'咋还扯上运动了','<p> 两妯娌在吵架，一个说：嗨，你男人像男足，一百年硬不起来，射不出来，憋死你。<br>　　另一个回应道：嗨，你男人像刘翔，前戏倒是很长，但一真刀实枪马上就仓皇撤退，馋死你。<br>　　这时候，婆婆过来劝架，插嘴道：哎呀，快别吵了，谁也没我可怜，你公爹这也不像，那也不像，偏偏像羽毛球队，到了晚上就玩消极比赛，哎...</p><p style=\"display:none;\" class=\"cloudreamHelperLink\" codetype=\"post\" entryid=\"2696\"></p>','','ADMIN','1423634815.42',NULL,NULL,1),(2420,'女儿长大了','<p> <span style=\"TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; DISPLAY: inline !important; FONT: 14px/24px 微软雅黑; WHITE-SPACE: normal; FLOAT: none; LETTER-SPACING: normal; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); WORD-SPACING: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">小琳：爸爸，我发现性生活和现实生活对嘴的要求完全不一样.</span><br style=\"TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; FONT: 14px/24px 微软雅黑; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); WORD-SPACING: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; DISPLAY: inline !important; FONT: 14px/24px 微软雅黑; WHITE-SPACE: normal; FLOAT: none; LETTER-SPACING: normal; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); WORD-SPACING: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">　　爸爸：是嘛，说来听听。</span><br style=\"TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; FONT: 14px/24px 微软雅黑; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); WORD-SPACING: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"TEXT-